ys%20of%20journey%20covering%20more%20than%203.8-lakh-km.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22CHETHAN%20KUMAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchandrayaan-3-isros-third-lunar-mission-successfully-launched-into-orbit%2Farticleshow%2F101754594.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20Chandrayaan-3%20Mission%20Lifts%20Off%2C%20Aims%20To%20Reach%20Moon%20In%2040%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Chandrayaan-3%20lifted%20off%20from%20Sriharikota%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20carrying%20the%20hopes%20of%20an%20entire%20nation.%20If%20successful%2C%20the%20mission%20will%20make%20India%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20achieve%20a%20controlled%20landing%20on%20the%20moon%2C%20after%20Russia%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20moon%20lander%20Vikram%20is%20perched%20on%20a%20Mark%203%20heavy-lift%20launch%20vehicle%20--%20dubbed%20the%20Bahubali%20rocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELVM3%20M4%2FChandrayaan-3%20Mission%3A%3Cbr%3E%5CnLVM3%20M4%20vehicle%F0%9F%9A%80%20successfully%20launched%20Chandrayaan-3%F0%9F%9B%B0%EF%B8%8F%20into%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20ISRO%20(%40isro)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%2Fstatus%2F1679783216230858754%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2014%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20from%20Earth%20to%20the%20moon%20for%20the%20spacecraft%20is%20estimated%20to%20take%20about%20a%20month%20and%20the%20landing%20is%20expected%20on%20August%2023.%20Upon%20landing%2C%20it%20will%20operate%20for%20one%20lunar%20day%2C%20which%20is%20approximately%2014%20Earth%20days.%20One%20day%20on%20the%20Moon%20is%20equal%20to%2014%20days%20on%20Earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-launch-live-updates-chandrayaan-3-to-lift-off-today-for-6-week-journey-to-moon-4206120%5C%22%3EChandrayaan-3%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20have%20three%20major%20components%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lander%2C%20a%20rover%2C%20and%20a%20propulsion%20model.%20It%20will%20be%20using%20the%20Orbiter%20from%20Chandrayaan-2%20which%20still%20exists%20in%20the%20lunar%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20first%2C%20India's%20mooncraft%20'Vikram'%20will%20land%20in%20the%20South%20Pole%20of%20the%20moon%2C%20where%20water%20molecules%20have%20been%20found.%20The%20finding%2C%20made%20during%20India's%20first%20moon%20mission%20in%202008%2C%20had%20startled%20the%20world.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikram%20is%20meant%20to%20have%20a%20safe%2C%20soft%20landing.%20The%20lander%20will%20then%20release%20the%20rover%20Pragyan%2C%20which%20will%20roam%20the%20moon's%20surface%20for%20a%20lunar%20day%20--%20equal%20to%2014%20earth%20days%20--%20and%20conduct%20scientific%20experiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-to-lift-off-today-for-the-6-week-journey-to-moon-10-points-4205795%5C%22%3Elatest%20iteration%20of%20the%20Chandrayaan%3C%2Fa%3E%20comes%20four%20years%20after%20an%20earlier%20attempt%20failed%2C%20with%20the%20ground%20crew%20losing%20contact%20moments%20before%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ISRO's%20second%20lunar%20mission%20Chandrayaan-2%20failed%20while%20attempting%20to%20land%20in%202019.%20However%2C%20to%20avoid%20past%20failures%2C%20ISRO%20has%20corporate%20a%20series%20of%20changes%20in%20the%20upcoming%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20main%20lacuna%20in%20the%20last%20Chandrayaan-2%20mission%20was%20that%20there%20were%20off-nominal%20conditions%20that%20were%20initiated%20in%20the%20system.%20Everything%20was%20not%20nominal.%20And%20the%20craft%20was%20not%20able%20to%20handle%20the%20off-nominal%20condition%20for%20a%20safe%20landing%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20Chief%20S%20Somnath%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689326580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fbclq29l_chandrayaan-3-liftoff_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-chandrayaan-3-mission-lifts-off-aims-to-reach-moon-in-40-days-4206754%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20Chandrayaan-3%20lifted%20off%20from%20Sriharikota%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20carrying%20the%20hopes%20of%20an%20entire%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-chandrayaan-3-mission-lifts-off-aims-to-reach-moon-in-40-days-4206754%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-chandrayaan-3-mission-lifts-off-aims-to-reach-moon-in-40-days-4206754%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-chandrayaan-3-mission-lifts-off-aims-to-reach-moon-in-40-days-4206754%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandrayaan-3%20Launched%20Successfully%3A%20Here's%20When%20It%20Will%20Land%20On%20The%20Moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%2C%20India's%20third%20mission%20to%20moon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-chandrayaan-3-mission-lifts-off-aims-to-reach-moon-in-40-days-4206754%5C%22%3Elaunched%20successfully%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Satish%20Dhawan%20space%20centre%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Sriharikota%20today.%20It%20is%20a%20major%20stride%20for%20India's%20space%20journey%2C%20which%20has%20expanded%20rapidly%20since%20the%20first%20moon%20mission%20in%202008.%20Its%20lander%20Vikram%20will%20be%20taken%20for%20landing%20on%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole%20by%20rover%20Pragyan.%20The%20primary%20objective%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20to%20prove%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20organisation's%20(ISRO's)%20capability%20of%20completing%20a%20soft%20landing%20on%20the%20moon.%20It%20is%20also%20carrying%20many%20important%20payloads%20that%20will%20collect%20important%20data%20about%20the%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landing%20will%20take%20place%20on%20August%2023-24%2C%20after%20a%2040-day%20journey.%20The%20date%20has%20been%20decided%20based%20on%20the%20availability%20of%20sunlight%20on%20the%20moon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20days%20when%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole%20is%20devoid%20of%20any%20sunlight%2C%20making%20it%20impossible%20for%20the%20solar%20panels%20attached%20to%20the%20lander%20to%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20date%20is%20missed%20due%20to%20any%20reason%2C%20ISRO%20will%20have%20to%20keep%20the%20landing%20for%20the%20next%20month%20-%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3%20will%20make%20India%20the%20fourth%20country%20after%20US%2C%20China%2C%20and%20Russia%2C%20to%20land%20its%20spacecraft%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20moon%20and%20demonstrate%20the%20country's%20abilities%20for%20safe%20and%20soft%20landing%20on%20lunar%20surface.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20lander%2C%20a%20rover%20and%20a%20propulsion%20module%20and%20weighs%20around%203%2C900%20kilograms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20remarkable%20mission%20will%20carry%20the%20hopes%20and%20dreams%20of%20our%20nation%2C%26quot%3B%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20tweeted%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrayaan-3's%20development%20phase%20commenced%20in%20January%202020%20with%20the%20launch%20planned%20sometime%20in%202021.%20However%2C%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%20brought%20an%20unforeseen%20delay%20to%20the%20mission's%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689326580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fl7gia45_chandrayaan3-launch-successful-1200_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-launched-successfully-heres-when-it-will-land-on-th