cturing-engineering-brain-drain-study-2023-6%5C%22%3Emanaging%20their%20supply%20chains%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20improving%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fveriti-used-this-14-slide-pitch-deck-to-raise-a-12-million-series-a-2022-11%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%20defenses%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20new%20partnership%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-investing-billions-into-chatgpt-creator-openai-partnership-2023-1%5C%22%3Ewith%20Microsoft%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20KPMG%20will%20invest%20%242%20billion%20over%20five%20years%20into%20the%20team%20effort%2C%20Carl%20Carande%2C%20US%20vice%20chair%20and%20global%20head%20of%20KPMG%20Advisory%2C%20told%20Insider.%20Microsoft%20didn't%20put%20a%20monetary%20figure%20on%20its%20part%20of%20the%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThrough%20their%20tie-up%2C%20the%20companies%20plan%20to%20jointly%20develop%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgenerative-ai-artificial-intelligence-jobs-work-careers-high-earners-mckinsey-2023-6%5C%22%3Egenerative%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20KPMG's%20employees%20and%20clients%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20some%20of%20the%20legacy%20ways%20of%20doing%20business%20executing%20services%20are%20going%20to%20become%20obsolete%2C%26quot%3B%20Carande%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20AI%20can%20help%20companies%20use%20information%20like%20market%20trends%20and%20sales%20data%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20they%20should%20be%20stocking%20products%20so%20their%20inventory%20is%20meeting%20demands%2C%20Carande%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20can%20help%20analyze%20historical%20data%2C%20identify%20patterns%2C%20and%20detect%20correlations%20that%20may%20not%20be%20apparent%20to%20human%20analysts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20cybersecurity%20defense%20front%2C%20generative%20AI%20can%20help%20interpret%20a%20range%20of%20data%20to%20provide%20quicker%20information%20about%20potential%20threats%20and%20how%20to%20respond%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20human%20with%20experience%2C%20intuition%2C%20and%20insider%20knowledge%20is%20still%20essential%20for%20picking%20out%20hard-to-detect%20anomalies%2C%26quot%3B%20Carande%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20generative%20AI%20provides%20a%20huge%20head%20start.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKPMG%20advises%20banks%20and%20financial%20institutions%2C%20energy%20companies%2C%20local%20governments%20around%20the%20world%2C%20and%20companies%20across%20industries%2C%20according%20to%20its%20website.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20employees%20in%20the%20US%20are%20already%20using%20generative%20AI%20chat%20tools%2C%20which%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ceo-worst-case-ai-lights-out-for-all-2023-1%5C%22%3Edeveloped%20with%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20technology%2C%20to%20perform%20tasks%20like%20drafting%20content%2C%20creating%20code%2C%20and%20summarizing%20documents%2C%20Carande%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20use%20of%20AI%20has%20not%20led%20to%20its%20layoffs%20so%20far%2C%20he%20said.%20KPMG%20had%20said%20it%20planned%20to%20let%20go%205%25%20of%20its%20employees%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffinance%2Fkpmg-cut-5-us-jobs-fresh-round-layoffs-2023-06-26%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DJune%252026%2520(Reuters)%2520%252D%2520KPMG%2C30.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported%20in%20June%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20Carande%20told%20Insider%20that%20AI%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20play%20into%20that%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuture%20considerations%20for%20hiring%20for%20certain%20roles%20in%20coding%2C%20writing%2C%20and%20research%20may%20change%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20continuing%20to%20grow%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20more%20professionals%2C%20but%20they're%20going%20to%20have%20a%20different%20level%20of%20technical%20acumen%20leveraging%20generative%20AI%2C%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20it's%20going%20to%20put%20them%20in%20a%20position%20to%20actually%20add%20more%20value%20faster%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20representative%20for%20Microsoft%20declined%20to%20comment%20beyond%20the%20companies'%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.microsoft.com%2F2023%2F07%2F11%2Fkpmg-and-microsoft-enter-landmark-agreement-to-put-ai-at-the-forefront-of-professional-services%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-microsoft-teaming-to-bring-more-ai-workplace-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689325380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b072c529e5fd00190eeee1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-microsoft-teaming-to-bring-more-ai-workplace-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22KPMG%20advises%20businesses%20around%20the%20world.%20It's%20teaming%20with%20Microsoft%20to%20bring%20AI%20to%20more%20of%20them.%20Get%20ready%20for%20the%20new%20tech%20to%20spread%20even%20faster.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sindhu%20Sundar)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkpmg-microsoft-teaming-to-bring-more-ai-workplace-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Jaiswal%20Runs%20To%20Rohit%20After%20Maiden%20Ton%2C%20Hugs%20Captain%20In%20Delight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20slammed%20an%20unbe