re's%20another%20interpretation%2C%20though%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20waning%20usage%20is%20caused%20by%20students%20on%20break%2C%20that's%20a%20bad%20sign%20because%20it%20suggests%20there's%20a%20smaller%20range%20of%20use%20cases%20for%20ChatGPT%20and%20other%20AI-powered%20chatbots%2C%20says%20Mark%20Shmulik%2C%20a%20top%20internet%20analyst%20at%20Bernstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20school%20kids%2C%20that's%20a%20real%20yellow-red%20flag%20on%20the%20size%20of%20the%20prize%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20this%20week.%20%26quot%3BThis%20idea%20that%20if%20the%20ChatGPT%20drop-off%20is%20due%20to%20students%20on%20summer%20break%2C%20that%20implies%20a%20narrower%20audience%20and%20fewer%20use%20cases.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20if%20a%20big%20part%20of%20ChatGPT%20growth%20is%20driven%20by%20cheating%20students%2C%20this%20means%20the%20technology%2C%20or%20at%20least%20the%20chatbot%20format%2C%20may%20not%20be%20the%20dominant%20computing%20platform%20of%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShmulik%20is%20a%20huge%20fan%20of%20this%20technology%2C%20but%20he's%20particularly%20perturbed%20by%20rising%20churn%20data.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ChatGPT%20chart%20shows%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20run%20out%20of%20new%20users%20and%20existing%20users%20churn%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Shmulik%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt's%20not%20all%20about%20chatbots%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20asked%20OpenAI%2C%20the%20creator%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20about%20all%20this%20on%20Thursday.%20I%20also%20pinged%20a%20spokesman%20for%20Microsoft%2C%20which%20is%20a%20major%20backer%20of%20OpenAI.%20OpenAI%20didn't%20respond.%20The%20Microsoft%20representative%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20reason%20for%20this%20ChatGPT%20dip%2C%20it%20does%20show%20that%20generative%20AI%20and%20large%20language%20models%20(LLMs)%20are%20not%20just%20about%20chatbots.%20There's%20so%20much%20more%20going%20on%20with%20this%20incredi