so%20excited%20to%20be%20on%20vacation%20again%20after%20spending%20what%20felt%20like%20an%20eternity%20at%20home%20that%20I%20acted%20careless%20with%20money%2C%20which%20was%20very%20unlike%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20I%20could%20have%20saved%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20money%20on%20my%20trip%20to%20Hawaii.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Travel%20during%20the%20off-season%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20Maui%20in%20the%20summer%2C%20which%20is%20a%20busy%20and%20expensive%20time.%20Off-season%20travel%20(also%20known%20as%20low%20or%20shoulder%20season)%20often%20means%20up%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nerdwallet.com%2Farticle%2Ftravel%2F5-reasons-why-shoulder-season-is-the-best-time-to-travel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E23%25%20cheaper%20flights%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20much%20better%20hotel%20and%20car%20rental%20prices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20notice%20fewer%20crowds%20at%20the%20beach%2C%20which%20is%20a%20welcomed%20bonus.%20The%20kicker%20is%20that%20peak%20season%20is%20most%20of%20the%20year%20in%20Hawaii%3A%20tourists%20flock%20to%20Hawaii%20from%20December%20to%20March%20to%20escape%20the%20cold%20and%20go%20whale-watching.%20June%20through%20August%20are%20busy%20because%20kids%20are%20out%20of%20school%20and%20the%20weather%20is%20the%20warmest%20with%20the%20least%20chance%20of%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpring%20and%20autumn%20are%20considered%20low%20seasons%2C%20and%20likely%20when%20you%20will%20find%20the%20best%20deals.%20Fair%20warning%3A%20Hawaii%20is%20at%20its%20rainiest%20from%20October%20to%20April%2C%20so%20check%20the%20average%20weather%20for%20the%20weeks%20you're%20planning%20to%20visit%20to%20know%20what%20to%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Pack%20at%20least%20one%20meal%20a%20day%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhenever%20travelers%2C%20especially%20in%20big%20groups%2C%20are%20interested%20in%20saving%20money%2C%20I%20always%20recommend%20finding%20accommodation%20with%20a%20kitchen%20or%20kitchenette%20and%20preparing%20some%20meals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20be%20spending%20anywhere%20from%20%2415-25%20or%20more%20per%20person%20dining%20at%20a%20restaurant%20for%20every%20meal.%20A%20quick%20grocery%20haul%20at%20Foodland%20or%20the%20farmer's%20market%20can%20give%20you%20the%20same%20fresh%20ingredients%20in%20your%20meals%20but%20just%20prepared%20at%20%26quot%3Bhome.%26quot%3B%20Also%2C%20Foodland%20is%20known%20for%20their%20delicious%20%E2%80%94%20and%20quite%20affordable%20%E2%80%94%20poke%20bowls.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20breakfast%20and%20lunch%20are%20the%20easiest%20to%20throw%20together%20and%20either%20eat%20quickly%20at%20your%20hotel%2C%20or%20bring%20with%20you%20to%20the%20beach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20way%2C%20if%20you're%20looking%20for%20the%20coveted%20Maui%20Gold%20pineapple%2C%20we%20didn't%20find%20it%20in%20any%20grocery%20stores%2C%20so%20check%20out%20local%20farmer's%20market%20for%20the%20delectable%20fruit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20DIY%20a%20snorkel%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jesse%20Collier%20snorkeling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b04b5d9751e300192a03e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJesse%20Collier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3EWe%20went%20on%20two%20catamaran%20snorkel%20excursions%3A%20one%20to%20Coral%20Gardens%20and%20one%20to%20the%20Molokini%20Crater.%C2%A0%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20honest%2C%20the%20Coral%20Gardens%20tour%20was%20underwhelming%3A%20the%20murky%20waters%20didn't%20do%20the%20coral%20justice%20(admittedly%2C%20I%20am%20spoiled%20from%20snorkeling%20in%20clear%20Caribbean%20waters)%20and%20it%20was%20extremely%20windy%2C%20which%20sucks%20when%20trying%20to%20eat%20lunch%20on%20a%20boat.%20To%20add%20salt%20to%20the%20wound%2C%20we%20didn't%20see%20any%20turtles%20or%20much%20wildlife%20at%20all.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20trip%20to%20Molokini%20was%20better%2C%20but%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20see%20some%20turtles%2C%20and%20didn't%20see%20any%20on%20those%20two%20trips.%20We%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20%24352%20for%20these%20snorkeling%20tours%2C%20which%2C%20when%20you%20consider%20it%20costs%20%2415%20to%20rent%20a%20snorkel%20kit%2C%20was%20a%20bitter%20pill%20to%20swallow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20tours%20will%20take%20you%20to%20what%20they%20call%20%26quot%3BTurtle%20Town%26quot%3B%20but%20I%20spoke%20with%20a%20local%20who%20said%20Makena%20Surf%2C%20near%20Wailea%2C%20is%20considered%20Turtle%20Town.%20She%20also%20recommended%20Airport%20Beach%2C%20Honolua%20Bay%2C%20and%20Kapalua%20Bay%20to%20see%20some%20turtles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20story%20short%3A%20you%20don't%20need%20a%20snorkeling%20tour%20to%20see%20some%20cool%20wildlife%2C%20just%20head%20over%20to%20Boss%20Frog%20and%20rent%20some%20snorkels.%20We%20even%20got%20lucky%20a%20few%20times%20and%20saw%20turtles%20hanging%20out%20at%20the%20beach!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Bring%20a%20portable%20coffee%20maker%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20hotels%20and%20rentals%20often%20have%20a%20coffee%20machine%2C%20but%20do%20you%20really%20want%20to%20drink%20that%20coffee%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20fact%20that%20those%20machines%20reportedly%20almost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thekitchn.com%2Fcoffee-maker-hotel-room-23345832%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enever%20get%20cleaned%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20coffee%20is%20pretty%20horrendous.%20Pack%20a%20bag%20of%20pre-ground%20specialty%20beans%20and%20an%20aeropress%20or%20drip%20coffee%20cup%20and%2C%20as%20long%20as%20you%20either%20have%20a%20microwave%2C%20kettle%2C%20or%20stove%20to%20heat%20up%20some%20water%2C%20you'll%20have%20quality%20coffee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20runs%20a%20coffee%20shop%20and%20was%20so%20burnt%20out%2C%20he%20decided%20he%20didn't%20want%20to%20make%20coffee%20at%20all%20on%20this%20trip.%20And%2C%20while%20I%20don't%20blame%20him%2C%20we%20definitely%20paid%20for%20it%2C%20with%20lattes%20costing%20around%20%246-8%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Rent%20a%20car%2015%20minutes%20away%20from%20the%20airport%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20visiting%20Hawaii%2C%20food%2C%20hotels%20and%20airfare%20aren't%20the%20only%20major%20expenses%3A%20we%20ended%20up%20paying%20about%20%24976%20for%20a%2010-day%20car%20rental.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20happened%20to%20be%20when%20there%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.staradvertiser.com%2F2021%2F06%2F13%2Fhawaii-news%2Fperfect-storm-in-hawaiis-rental-car-industry-shows-no-signs-of-clearing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextreme%20rental%20car%20shortage%3C%2Fa%3E%20nationwide%20so%20I%20had%20to%20take%20what%20I%20could%20get.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20to%20go%20back%2C%20I%20would%20schedule%20a%20rental%20car%20a%2015-minute%20taxi%20ride%20away%20from%20the%20airport%2C%20as%20it%20is%20said%20that%20pricing%20is%20much%20better%20the%20farther%20you%20get%20from%20the%20airport.%20If%20you%20want%20your%20car%20waiting%20for%20you%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20I%20don't%20blame%20you%2C%20but%20you%20pay%20a%20premium%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jesse%20Collier%20with%20shaved%20ice%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b04b93c22d1a001945567c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EJesse%20Collier%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Opt%20for%20more%20street%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20touristy%20locations%2C%20Hawaii%20has%20some%20amazing%20street%20food%3A%20poke%2C%20shave%20ice%2C%20acai%20bowls%2C%20spam%20musubi%2C%20manapua%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20While%20we%20did%20try%20a%20few%2C%20we%20definitely%20would%20have%20saved%20some%20money%20if%20we%20spent%20less%20time%20in%20sit-down%20restaurants%20and%20more%20time%20devouring%20street%20food%20on%20a%20bench%2C%20feeling%20the%20ocean%20breeze.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20plenty%20of%20YouTube%20videos%20and%20blogs%20on%20the%20best%20street%20food%20on%20every%20Hawaiian%20island%20if%20you'd%20like%20a%20little%20guidance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E7.%20Take%20public%20transportation%20instead%20of%20renting%20a%20car%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20know%2C%20car%20rentals%20are%20a%20pretty%20penny%2C%20but%20Oahu%2C%20Maui%2C%20Kauai%2C%20and%20the%20Big%20Island%20have%20public%20transportation%20systems.%20If%20taking%20the%20bus%20is%20a%20must%20for%20your%20budget%2C%20I%20recommend%20looking%20into%20the%20transportation%20lines%20of%20each%20of%20these%20areas%20and%20seeing%20if%20you%20can%20easily%20get%20to%20all%20the%20places%20you'd%20like%20to%20visit.%20If%20there%20are%20a%20few%20short%20distances%20here%20and%20there%20that%20the%20bus%20won't%20take%20you%20to%2C%20calling%20an%20Uber%20or%20Lyft%20is%20always%20an%20option.%20Be%20sure%20to%20budget%20for%20the%20required%20fares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHawaii%20is%20an%20incredible%20destination%20for%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20whether%20you%20are%20bunking%20at%20a%20bare-bones%20hostel%20or%20lounging%20at%20a%20luxury%20resort.%20It%20is%20known%20to%20be%20expensive%2C%20and%20these%20costs%20will%20definitely%20add%20up%2C%20but%20implementing%20these%20tips%20will%20alleviate%20some%20of%20the%20financial%20burden.%20Instead%20of%20experiencing%20a%20credit%20card%20statement%20jump-scare%2C%20you%20can%20return%20from%20Hawaii%20relaxed%2C%20rested%2C%20and%2C%20let's%20be%20honest%2C%20a%20little%20sunburnt.%20Worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Csection%20data-track-content%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-post-type%3D%5C%22post