tions.%20They%20were%20spotted%20outside%20Parineeti's%20house%20last%20night%20as%20they%20rushed%20somewhere.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221st%20Time%20In%20Indian%20History!%20Rohit%2C%20Jaiswal%20Script%20Never-Seen-Before%20Record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20229-run%20opening%20stand%20between%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20youngster%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20marked%20the%20first%20time%20in%20Test%20history%20when%20India%20took%20the%20lead%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20without%20losing%20a%20wicket%20on%20Thursday.%C2%A0India%20managed%20to%20restrict%20West%20Indies%20for%20a%20score%20of%20150%20runs%20on%20Day%201%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20at%20Windsor%20Park.%20In%20reply%20to%20the%20WI's%20total%2C%20Rohit%20and%20Jaiswal%20went%20on%20to%20score%20a%20century%20each%20which%20allowed%20India%20to%20take%20a%20commanding%20position%20in%20the%20two-match%20Test%20series.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20229-run%20opening%20stand%20between%20Rohit%20and%20Jaiswal%20is%20also%20the%20second-highest%20for%20India%20in%20Tests%20in%20West%20Indies.%20The%20record%20is%20held%20by%20Vijay%20Manjrekar%20and%20Pankaj%20Roy%2C%20who%20put%20on%20237%20for%20the%20second%20wicket%20at%20Sabina%20Park%20in%201953.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20partnership%20was%20also%20the%20highest%20opening%20partnership%20for%20India%20vs%20West%20Indies.%20Earlier%2C%20Virender%20Sehwag%20and%20Sanjay%20Bangar%20held%20the%20record%20with%20a%20partnership%20of%20159%20runs%20in%202006.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResuming%20their%20innings%20at%2080%2F0%20on%20Day%202%2C%20India%20openers%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20debutant%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20kept%20the%20scoreboard%20ticking.%20The%20batting%20pair%20of%20Rohit%20and%20Yashasvi%20were%20decisive%20in%20their%20approach%20and%20made%20the%20West%20Indies%20bowlers%20toil%20hard%20making%20merry%20of%20the%20excellent%20batting%20conditions%20on%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDebutant%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20brought%20up%20his%20fifty%20soon%20after%20the%20day's%20play%20began%20while%20the%20India%20captain%20continued%20to%20pile%20up%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20batters%20rotated%20the%20strike%20brilliantly%2C%20not%20allowing%20the%20Windies%20bowlers%20to%20settle%20down%20while%20whacking%20the%20loose%20balls%20on%20offer.%20Rohit%20was%20the%20aggressor%20of%20the%20batting%20pair%2C%20smashing%20boundaries%20regularly.%20The%20Indian%20opening%20pair%20completely%20dominated%20the%20West%20Indies%20bowlers%20as%20runs%20came%20thick%20and%20fast%20for%20the%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlzarri%20Joseph%20was%20on%20the%20receiving%20end%20with%20Rohit%20smashing%20him%20for%20two%20boundaries%20and%20one%20maximum%20in%20an%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20displayed%20great%20resilience%20and%20determination%20as%20he%20brought%20up%20his%20fifty%20in%20the%2038th%20over%20of%20the%20game.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20stay%20together%20on%20the%20pitch%20finally%20came%20to%20an%20end%20as%20debutant%20Alick%20Athanaze%20got%20wicket%20of%20the%20Indian%20skipper%2C%20and%20sent%20him%20back%20to%20the%20pavilion%20for%20a%20score%20of%20103.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaiswal%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20managed%20to%20survive%20till%20the%20umpires%20decided%20to%20call%20off%20the%20day.%20India%20walked%20away%20with%20a%20firm%20lead%20of%20162%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689323760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F846o2b2o_rohit-and-jaiswal-afp_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ffirst-time-in-indian-history-rohit-sharma-yashasvi-jaiswal-script-never-seen-before-test-record-4205812%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20put%20up%20229-run%20stand%20for%20the%20first%20wicket%20before%20the%20India%20skipper%20was%20dismissed%20on%20Day%202%20of%20the%20first%20Test%20against%20West%20Indies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ffirst-time-in-indian-history-rohit-sharma-yashasvi-jaiswal-script-never-seen-before-test-record-4205812%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ffirst-time-in-indian-history-rohit-sharma-yashasvi-jaiswal-script-never-seen-before-test-record-4205812%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwest-indies-vs-india-2023%2Ffirst-time-in-indian-history-rohit-sharma-yashasvi-jaiswal-script-never-seen-before-test-record-4205812%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20The%20Role%20Sun%20Will%20Play%20In%20Chandrayaan-3's%20Landing%20On%20Moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20less%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20India%20will%20make%20history%20by%20launching%20its%20third%20moon%20mission%2C%20called%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-to-lift-off-today-for-the-6-week-journey-to-moon-10-points-4205795%5C%22%3Eto%20explore%20the%20lunar%20surface%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20a%20follow-up%20mission%20to%20Chandrayaan-2%20and%20will%20land%20on%20the%20south%20pole%20of%20Earth's%20natural%20satellite%20after%20a%2040-day%20journey.%20According%20to%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20the%20soft-landing%20has%20been%20planned%20according%20to%20the%20availability%20of%20sunlight.%20This%20has%20been%20done%20since%20solar%20panel%20has%20been%20added%20to%20the%20lander.%20ISRO%20chief%20S%20Somanath%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20the%20additional%20solar%20panels%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20lander%20generates%20power%20no%20matter%20how%20it%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sunlight%20is%20very%20important.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20landing%20has%20been%20planned%20when%20sunlight%20is%20available.%20It%20is%20crucial%20that%20it%20stays%20for%20the%20day%20so%20that%20you%20can%20charge%20the%20solar%20panels%20and%20the%20rover%20can%20go%20around%2C%26quot%3B%20Annapurni%20Subramaniam%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Astrophysics%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20module%20will%20approximately%20take%20six%20weeks%20to%20reach%20the%20moon%20around%20August%2023.%20%26quot%3BThe%20date%20is%20decided%20based%20on%20when%20the%20sunrise%20is%20on%20the%20moon%3B%20it%20will%20depend%20on%20the%20calculations%2C%20but%20if%20it%20gets%20delayed%2C%20then%20we%20will%20have%20to%20keep%20the%20landing%20for%20the%20next%20month%20in%20September%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Somanath%20had%20said%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EISRO%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchandrayaan-3-will-not-repeat-the-mistakes-of-predecessor-isro-chief-4203387%5C%22%3Emade%20several%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20based%20on%20the%20lessons%20learnt%20from%20the%20failure%20of%20Chandrayaan-2%20that%20failed%20in%20September%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20scenarios%20including%20engine%20failure%2C%20sensor%20failure%2C%20calculation%20failure%2C%20and%20algorithm%20failure%20were%20examined%20and%20measures%20developed%20to%20counteract%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20added%20new%20instruments%20to%20handle%20failures%2C%20new%20algorithms%20to%20handle%20off-nominal%20situations%2C%20new%20approaches%20to%20soft%20land%20in%20case%20of%20not-availability%2C%20any%20such%20measurements%20and%20total%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Somanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20difference%20is%20the%20apparatus%20on%20the%20orbiters.%20While%20the%20Chandrayaan-2%20orbiter%20carried%209%20instruments%2C%20the%20new%20orbiter%20will%20have%20a%20lone%20in-situ%20instrument%3A%20Spectro-polarimetry%20of%20habitable%20planet%20Earth%20(SHAPE).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20space%20programme%20has%20grown%20considerably%20in%20size%20and%20momentum%20since%20it%20first%20sent%20a%20probe%20to%20orbit%20the%20moon%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689323580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fqsa4quds_chandrayaan3-pti_625x300_10_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-the-role-sun-will-play-in-chandrayaan-3s-landing-on-moon-4206701%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22ISRO%20has%20made%20changes%20to%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20based%20on%20the%20lessons%20learnt%20from%20the%20failure%20of%20Chandrayaan-2%20that%20failed%20in%20September%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-the-role-sun-will-play-in-chandrayaan-3s-landing-on-moon-4206701%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-the-role-sun-will-play-in-chandrayaan-3s-landing-on-moon-4206701%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-the-role-sun-will-play-in-chandrayaan-3s-landing-on-moon-4206701%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Delhi's%20Migrant%20Worker%20Settlements%2C%20the%20Poor%20Remain%20Poor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14123330%2F2.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20twin%20settlements%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0264275122000300%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EKapashera%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C