he%20goal%20of%20ending%20TB%2C%20the%20organisation%20said%20adding%20that%20the%20tender%20for%20bedaquiline%20will%20be%20launched%20by%20end-July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20patent%20office%20in%20March%20this%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fjohnson-and-johnson-patent-tuberculosis-drug-bedaquiline%5C%22%3Erejected%20a%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20J%26amp%3BJ%20to%20extend%20its%20primary%20patent%2C%20which%20expires%20this%20month.%20Generic%20manufacturers%20will%20now%20be%20able%20to%20make%20their%20own%20versions%20in%20India%20at%20an%20affordable%20price%20that%20will%20likely%20be%2080%25%20cheaper%20for%20a%20six-month%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJ%26amp%3BJ%20had%20filed%20a%20patent%20for%20the%20fumarate%20salt%20of%20bedaquiline%20in%202008%20to%20extend%20its%20patent%20till%20the%20end%20of%202027.%20The%20move%20was%20part%20of%20a%20strategy%20called%20patent%20evergreening%2C%20through%20which%20companies%20%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eextend%20patent%20rights%20and%20keep%20drug%20prices%20high.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20highest%20TB%20burden%20and%20the%20government%20has%20announced%20an%20ambitious%20plan%20to%20end%20the%20disease%20by%202030%20%E2%80%93%20although%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmansukh-mandaviya-india-tb-elimination-2025-survey-report-disagrees%2F%5C%22%3Edoubts%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20deadline%20will%20be%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20WHO%20plans%20to%20eliminate%20TB%20by%202030%2C%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-tb-eradication-downslide-who-report%5C%22%3Edelivered%20a%20setback%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20tackling%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrenda%20Waning%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20Global%20Drug%20Facility%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fwillskipworth%2F2023%2F07%2F13%2Fjohnson--johnson-letting-nonprofit-distribute-life-saving-generic-tuberculosis-drug-greatly-expanding-access-in-poorer-countries%2F%3Fsh%3D1797a7eb3dcd%5C%22%3Etold%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20agreement%20gives%20them%20the%20ability%20to%20%E2%80%9Csell%20generic%20versions%20of%20the%20drug%20in%2044%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Mozambique%2C%20the%20Philippines%20and%20Zambia%E2%80%9D%2C%20countries%20where%20the%20patent%20is%20active.%20In%2052%20countries%2C%20Global%20Drug%20Facility%20already%20sells%20generic%20drugs%20because%20Johnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%E2%80%99s%20patents%20have%20expired%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaning%20added%20that%20discussions%20have%20already%20taken%20place%20with%20two%20Indian%20manufacturers%20%E2%80%93%20Lupin%20and%20Macleods%20%E2%80%93%20%C2%A0to%20produce%20the%20drug.%20Global%20Drug%20Facility%20will%20accept%20bids%20and%20select%20a%20primary%20and%20secondary%20manufacturer%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%20added%20that%20the%20agreement%20will%20not%20apply%20to%20some%20countries%20in%20eastern%20Europe%20and%20Asia%2C%20where%20J%26amp%3BJ%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpharmstd.com%2Farchivedetails_64_2747.html%5C%22%3Eestablished%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20exclusive%20agreement%20with%20Russian%20pharmaceutical%20company%20Pharmstandard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%20%26amp%3B%20Johnson%20charges%20%24272%20(~Rs%2022%2C000)%20for%20the%20total%20six-month%20course%20needed%20to%20treat%20TB%20but%20a%20study%20published%20in%202017%20estimated%20that%20if%20generic%20versions%20of%20bedaquiline%20enter%20the%20market%2C%20the%20price%20would%20fall%20to%20somewhere%20between%20%2448-%24102%20(~Rs%204%2C000%20to%20~Rs%208%2C300).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689322448000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2F02171246%2FMycobacterium_tuberculosis_Bacteria_the_Cause_of_TB_5149398656.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fbreakthrough-jj-distribute-generic-tb-drug-bedaquiline%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22TB%20causes%201.5%20million%20deaths%20every%20year%2C%20despite%20being%20treatable.%20It%20is%20the%20world's%20deadliest%20infectious%20disease%20and%20among%20the%20top%20causes%20of%20death%20globally.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fbreakthrough-jj-distribute-generic-tb-drug-bedaquiline%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Miracle%5C%22%3A%20Israeli%20Doctors%20Reattach%20Boy's%20Head%20After%20He%20Was%20Hit%20By%20A%20Car%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20is%20being%20dubbed%20a%20%26quot%3Bmiracle%26quot%3B%2C%20doctors%20in%20Israel%20performed%20an%20extremely%20unusual%20and%20complicated%20surgery%20on%20a%2012-year-boy%20where%20they%20reattached%20his%20head%20to%20his%20neck%20after%20he%20was%20hit%20by%20a%20car%20while%20riding%20a%20bicycle%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fhadassah-surgeons-reattach-boys-head-to-his-neck-after-internal-decapitation%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuleiman%20Hassan%20suffered%20an%20%26quot%3Binternal%20decapitation%26quot%3B%2C%20where%20his%20skull%20detached%20from%20the%20top%20vertebrae%20of%20his%20spine%20after%20a%20car%20accident%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%20The%20condition%20is%20scientifically%20known%20as%20a%20bilateral%20atlanto%20occipital%20joint%20dislocation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20accident%2C%20the%20boy%20was%20airlifted%20to%20Hadassah%20Medical%20Center%2C%20where%20he%20was%20sent%20for%20emergency%20surgery.%20As%20per%20the%20doctors%2C%20his%20head%20was%20%26quot%3Balmost%20completely%20detached%20from%20the%20base%20of%20his%20neck.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Ohad%20Einav%2C%20the%20orthopaedic%20surgeon%20who%20oversaw%20the%20treatment%2C%20%C2%A0told%20The%20Times%20of%20Israel%20that%20it%20took%20several%20hours%20and%20necessitated%20the%20placement%20of%20%26quot%3Bnew%20plates%20and%20fixations%20in%20the%20damaged%20area.%20%26quot%3BOur%20ability%20to%20save%20the%20child%20was%20thanks%20to%20our%20knowledge%20and%20the%20most%20innovative%20technology%20in%20the%20operating%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20team%20%26quot%3Bfought%20for%20the%20boy's%20life.%26quot%3B%20The%20surgeons%20also%20believe%20that%20his%20recovery%20was%20no%20less%20than%20a%20miracle%20as%20the%20boy%20only%20had%20a%2050%20per%20cent%20chance%20of%20survival.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20procedure%20took%20place%20last%20month%2C%20however%2C%20the%20doctors%20didn't%20make%20the%20results%20public%20until%20July.%20Mr%20Hassan%20was%20recently%20discharged%20from%20the%20hospital%20with%20a%20cervical%20splint%20and%20the%20hospital%20stated%20that%20they%20will%20continue%20to%20monitor%20his%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20such%20a%20child%20has%20no%20neurological%20deficits%20or%20sensory%20or%20motor%20dysfunction%20and%20that%20he%20is%20functioning%20normally%20and%20walking%20without%20an%20aid%20after%20such%20a%20long%20process%20is%20no%20small%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Einav%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20the%20extremely%20rare%20surgery%20needs%20specialised%20doctors%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Blarge%20size%20of%20a%20child's%20head%20relative%20to%20an%20adult%20means%20they%20are%20more%20susceptible.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20common%20surgery%20at%20all%2C%20and%20especially%20not%20on%20children%20and%20teens.%20A%20surgeon%20needs%20knowledge%20and%20experience%20to%20do%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy's%20father%20did%20not%20leave%20his%20son%20a