v.com%2Findia-news%2Ftomato-prices-tomato-price-hike-delhi-may-get-cheaper-tomatoes-this-weekend-heres-how-4199909%5C%22%3Esoaring%20prices%20of%20the%20kitchen%20staple%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20touched%20record%20highs%20recently.%20However%2C%20each%20person%20can%20buy%20only%202%20kgs%20of%20tomato%20per%20head%20on%20subsidised%20rates.%20Freshly%20procured%20tomatoes%20arrived%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20overnight%20from%20%3Cem%3Emandis%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20key%20growing%20states%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20and%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stocks%20of%20tomato%20will%20be%20distributed%20through%20retail%20outlets%20at%20%26quot%3Bdiscounted%20prices%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20consumers%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%20region%20by%20Friday%2C%20this%20week%2C%20an%20official%20release%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Noida%2C%20tomatoes%20will%20be%20sold%20at%20the%20NCCF%20office%20at%20Rajnigandha%20Chowk%20and%20also%20through%20mobile%20vans%20in%20Greater%20Noida%20and%20other%20locations%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCCF%20will%20start%20the%20sale%20in%20other%20cities%20such%20as%20Lucknow%2C%20Kanpur%20and%20Jaipur%20during%20the%20weekend%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20NCCF%20started%20the%20sale%20on%20Friday%20in%20all%2011%20districts%20through%2020%20mobile%20vans%20and%20five%20centres.%20About%2017%2C000%20kg%20of%20tomatoes%20will%20be%20sold%20in%20total%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%C2%A0NCCF%20Chairman%20Vishal%20Singh%20told%20NDTV%2C%20clarifying%20that%20the%20subsidised%20rates%20will%20be%20capped%20at%202%20kgs%20for%20every%20customer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20NCCF%20plans%20to%20sell%20about%2020%2C000%20kg%20of%20tomatoes%20and%20the%20quantity%20will%20be%20increased%20to%2040%2C000%20per%20day%20as%20the%20sale%20picks%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20had%20on%20Wednesday%20directed%20its%20agricultural%20marketing%20agencies%20--%20National%20Agricultural%20Cooperative%20Marketing%20Federation%20of%20India%20(NAFED)%20and%20National%20Cooperative%20Consumers'%20Federation%20of%20India%20(NCCF)%20--%20to%20start%20immediate%20procurement%20of%20tomatoes%20in%20order%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20consumers%20who%20were%20forced%20to%20buy%20it%20for%20as%20high%20as%20Rs%20150%20to%20160%20per%20kg%20in%20the%20past%20month.%20It%20even%20went%20up%20to%20Rs%20224%20per%20kg%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20a%20massive%20increase%20from%20the%20usual%20Rs%2020-30%20per%20kg%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENCCF%20Managing%20Director%20Anice%20Joseph%20Chandra%20has%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20fixed%20the%20price%20at%20Rs%2090%20per%20kg%2C%20while%20the%20procurement%20rate%20is%20Rs%20120-130%20per%20kg.%20The%20losses%20will%20be%20absorbed%20by%20the%20central%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20attributed%20the%20sharp%20rise%20in%20prices%20to%20the%20monsoon%20season%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20added%20to%20further%20challenges%20related%20to%20distribution%20and%20increased%20transit%20losses.%20Tomatoes%20have%20a%20relatively%20lower%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20periods%20during%20July-August%20and%20October-November%20are%20generally%20the%20lean%20production%20months%20for%20tomato.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20southern%20and%20western%20regions%20of%20India%20accounts%20for%2056-58%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20tomato%20production%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSouthern%20and%20Western%20regions%2C%20being%20surplus%20states%2C%20feed%20to%20other%20markets%20depending%20on%20production%20seasons.%20The%20production%20seasons%20are%20also%20different%20across%20regions.%20The%20peak%20harvesting%20season%20occurs%20from%20December%20to%20February%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20food%20ministry%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20cycle%20of%20planting%20and%20harvesting%20seasons%20and%20variation%20across%20regions%20are%20primarily%20responsible%20for%20price%20seasonality%20in%20Tomato.%20Apart%20from%20the%20normal%20price%20seasonality%2C%20temporary%20supply%20chain%20disruptions%20and%20crop%20damage%20due%20to%20adverse%20weather%20conditions%20etc.%20often%20lead%20to%20sudden%20spikes%20in%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20database%20maintained%20by%20the%20Price%20Monitoring%20Division%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Consumer%20Affairs%2C%20per%20kilogram%20tomato%20on%20average%20rose%20by%20Rs%2060-100%20this%20month%20of%20what%20they%20were%20in%20retail%20markets%20in%20early%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EData%20showed%20prices%20of%20tomatoes%20in%20Delhi%20going%20up%20exponentially%20from%20Rs%2020%20per%20kg%20in%20early%20June%20to%20Rs%20110%20last%20week.%20Similarly%2C%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Ahmedabad%2C%20and%20Kolkata%2C%20three%20key%20consuming%20regions%2C%20the%20prices%20per%20kilogram%20rose%20to%20Rs%20117%2C%20Rs%20100%2C%20and%20Rs%20148.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689322320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fgs6d7d1_tomato_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftomato-prices-live-tomato-cost-today-in-huge-relief-on-soaring-tomato-prices-centre-starts-sale-today-at-4206227%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20will%20start%20selling%20tomatoes%20at%20Rs%2090%20per%20kg%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20Lucknow%2C%20Patna%2C%20and%20other%20chosen%20big%20cities%20across%20the%20country%2C%20to%20combat%20soaring%20prices%20of%20the%20kitchen%20staple%2C%20which%20went%20up%20to%20record%20highs%20recently%2C%20pinching%20consumers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftomato-prices-live-tomato-cost-today-in-huge-relief-on-soaring-tomato-prices-centre-starts-sale-today-at-4206227%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2F