n-3-akshay-kumar-anupam-kher-riteish-deshmukkh-cheer-for-isro-scientists%2Farticleshow%2F101748583.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Will%20Hand%20Over%20Government%20To%20Caretaker%20Set-Up%20In%20August%3A%20Pak%20PM%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20has%20said%20that%20he%20will%20be%20handing%20over%20the%20government%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccaretaker%20set-up%E2%80%9D%20in%20August%2C%20once%20the%20term%20of%20the%20assembly%20ends%2C%20Dawn%20reported%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20made%20a%20similar%20announcement%20yesterday%20as%20well%2C%20in%20which%20he%20declared%20that%20the%20term%20of%20his%20government%20would%20end%20on%20August%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Sharif%20did%20not%20make%20it%20clear%20whether%20the%20coalition%20partners%20would%20go%20for%20the%20normal%20dissolution%20of%20the%20National%20Assembly%20(NA)%20on%20completion%20of%20its%20term%20on%20August%2012%20or%20he%20would%20advise%20the%20president%20for%20an%20early%20dissolution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five-year%20term%20of%20the%20NA%20commenced%20under%20the%20then-PTI%20government%20on%20August%2012%2C%202018%20and%20will%20be%20completed%20under%20a%20PM-Shehbaz-led%20ruling%20coalition%20following%20the%20ouster%20of%20former%20premier%20Imran%20Khan%20through%20a%20no-confidence%20vote%20in%20April%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20outset%20of%20an%20address%20%E2%80%94%20broadcast%20on%20television%20%E2%80%94%20PM%20Sharif%20said%20he%20was%20given%20the%20%E2%80%9Csacred%20responsibility%E2%80%9D%20of%20running%20the%20country%20and%20%E2%80%9Cworking%20for%20its%20welfare%E2%80%9D%20in%20April%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20hand%20over%20this%20responsibility%20to%20the%20caretaker%20set-up%20in%20August%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dawn%20quoted%20Sharif%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20incumbent%20government%2C%20in%20mere%2015%20months%20of%20its%20brief%20tenure%2C%20cleaned%20the%20%E2%80%9Crubble%20of%20destruction%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwork%20of%20the%20PTI%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20last%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharif%20added%20that%20during%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20his%20government%20%E2%80%9Csacrificed%20politics%20to%20protect%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20said%20that%20the%20coalition%20government's%20tenure%20will%20end%20on%20August%2014%20and%20the%20date%20for%20the%20next%20polls%20will%20be%20announced%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20Pakistan%20(ECP)%20either%20in%20%E2%80%9COctober%20or%20November%E2%80%9D%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government's%20tenure%20will%20end%20on%20August%2014%2C%20the%20election%20commission%20will%20decide%20when%20the%20polls%20will%20take%20place%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20in%20October%20or%20November%2C%26quot%3B%20Geo%20News%20quoted%20Sharif%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhosoever%20forms%20the%20next%20government%20after%20elections%2C%20their%20top%20priority%20should%20be%20education%20so%20they%20can%20make%20this%20nation%20great%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Interior%20Minister%20Rana%20Sanaullah%20had%20also%20said%20the%20assemblies%20could%20be%20dissolved%20earlier%20than%20the%20scheduled%20date%20of%20August%2013%20to%20%26quot%3Bfacilitate%26quot%3B%20the%20ECP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20has%20also%20demanded%20the%20elections%20take%20place%20at%20their%20stipulated%20time%20as%20it%20is%20eyeing%20%26quot%3Bits%20victory%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20continues%20to%20be%20under%20pressure%20as%20the%20country%20is%20undergoing%20its%20worst%20economic%20crisis%2C%20inflation%20is