nder%2C%20former%20Deputy%20Mayor%20of%20Shimla%20Tikender%20Panwar%20and%20community%20leaders%20Shakeel%20Abdul%20and%20Akbar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20May%20a%20public%20hearing%20was%20held%20in%20which%20representatives%20from%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20Nagpur%2C%20Indore%20and%20Udaipur%2C%20apart%20from%20different%20slum%20colonies%20in%20Delhi%2C%20spoke%20the%20alleged%20brutality%20inflicted%20upon%20communities%20which%20were%20evicted%20by%20authorities%20with%20the%20G20%20events%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20observes%20that%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%E2%80%98distressing%E2%80%99%20instances%20of%20%3Cspan%3Eforced%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Eevictions%3C%2Fspan%3E%20that%20was%20covered%20at%20the%20public%20hearing%20was%20the%20demolition%20of%20homeless%20shelters%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fin-photos-for-g20-beautification-poor-families-living-along-the-yamuna-face-eviction%5C%22%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20Yamuna%20Pushta%20area%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20March%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Urban%20Shelter%20Improvement%20Board%3Cbr%3E%5Cndemolished%20eight%20of%20its%20own%20shelters%20near%20the%20Yamuna%20floodplains%2C%20leaving%20the%20homeless%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20live%20on%20the%20streets.%20The%20report%20says%20that%20a%20shelter%20at%20Sarai%20Kale%20Khan%20has%20also%20been%20removed%20apparently%20because%20a%20park%20has%20been%20constructed%20nearby%20%E2%80%93%20a%20venue%20to%20which%20%3Cspan%3EG20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20dignitaries%20will%20be%20brought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fas-india-prepares-to-host-g20-meet-delhis-most-vulnerable-have-been-rendered-homeless%5C%22%3EAs%20India%20Prepares%20to%20Host%20G20%20Meet%2C%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Vulnerable%20Have%20Been%20Rendered%20Homeless%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20information%20takes%20on%20new%20significance%20with%20the%20Yamuna%20swelling%20to%20record%20heights%20and%2C%20resultantly%2C%20flooding%20parts%20of%20Delhi%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20quotes%20Seema%2C%20a%20disabled%20mother%20whose%20living%20quarters%20in%20the%20shelter%20was%20destroyed.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20supply%20has%20also%20been%20stopped.%20Now%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20living%20under%20trees.%20I%20cannot%20move%20since%20%5Bmy%5D%20accident%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15150934%2FCart-getting-loaded-for-them-to-move-out-as-the-bulldozers-arrive.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15150934%2FCart-getting-loaded-for-them-to-move-out-as-the-bulldozers-arrive.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15150934%2FCart-getting-loaded-for-them-to-move-out-as-the-bulldozers-arrive-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F15150934%2FCart-getting-loaded-for-them-to-move-out-as-the-bulldozers-arrive-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-658341%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20family%20loads%20their%20belongings%20on%20a%20cart%20in%20case%20the%20bulldozers%20arrive.%20Photo%3A%20Shome%20Basu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20time%20between%20a%20notice%20and%20the%20demolition%20drive%20was%20little.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPuja%20from%20Bela%20Estate%20in%20Delhi%20also%20noted%20that%20demolishers%20broke%20the%20hand%20pumps%20so%20that%20they%20could%20leave%20within%20the%20three-hour%20window%20they%20were%20given%20to%20pack%20their%20things.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20students%20missed%20their%20board%E2%80%99s%20exam%20due%20to%20the%20eviction%20that%20took%20place%20on%2029th%20April%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20highlighted%20that%20even%20the%20Delhi%20urban%20minister%20was%20unaware%20of%20the%20drive%20and%20sought%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20CEO%20of%20DUSIB.%20After%20this%2C%20a%20new%20law%20was%20promulgated%20under%20which%20demolitions%20of%20shelters%20can%20only%20take%20place%20under%20the%20orders%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShakeel%20Abdul%20from%20Basti%20Suraksha%20Manch%20said%20250%2C000%20to%20300%2C000%20people%20were%20forcibly%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20Yamuna%20floodplains%2C%20Tughlaqabad%2C%20and%20Bela%20state%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%3EG20%3C%2Fspan%3E%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20erection%20of%20barricades%20also%20cut%20off%20access%20roads%20to%20these%20shelters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESucheta%20De%2C%20an%20activist%2C%20is%20quoted%20in%20the%20report%20as%20having%20said%20that%20Tuglaqabad%20looks%20as%20if%20%E2%80%9Can%20aerial%20bombardment%20has%20taken%20place%2C%20given%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20destruction.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20noted%20how%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20the%20G20%20inauguration%20meant%20that%20slums%20were%20being%20hidden%20behind%20iron%20sheets%20covered%20with%20plastic%20grass%20so%20that%20they%20appear%20%E2%80%9Cgreen%E2%80%9D.%20The%20city%E2%80%99s%20police%20commissioner%20issued%20a%20public%20order%20that%20no%20beggars%20must%20be%20visible%20at%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20crossroads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20Visakhapatnam%2C%205.5-foot%20tall%20green%20sheets%20extending%20