60-8314-6beb9d12c193.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bombay%20high%20court%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2010%20said%20that%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20should%20be%20distinguished%20from%20the%20age%20of%20marriage%20as%20consensual%20sexual%20acts%20can%20take%20place%20outside%20outside%20the%20latter.%20The%20court%20added%20that%20such%20relationships%20between%20minors%20should%20not%20be%20dealt%20with%20a%20punitive%20approach%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fbombay-high-court-sex-consent-age-teen-romance-pocso-act-age-of-marriage-232693%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Bharati%20Dangre%20raised%20concerns%20over%20criminalisation%20of%20romantic%20relationships%20between%20minors%20and%20urged%20for%20a%20progressive%20approach%20that%20enables%20their%20access%20to%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20services%20instead%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20mere%20apprehension%20that%20adolescents%20would%20make%20an%20impulsive%20and%20bad%20decision%2C%20cannot%20classify%20them%20under%20one%20head%20and%20by%20ignoring%20their%20will%20and%20wishes.%20The%20age%20of%20consent%20necessarily%20has%20to%20be%20distinguished%20from%20the%20age%20of%20marriage%20as%20sexual%20acts%20do%20not%20happen%20only%20in%20the%20confines%20of%20marriage%20and%20not%20only%20the%20society%2C%20but%20the%20judicial%20system%20must%20take%20note%20of%20this%20important%20aspect%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fbombay-high-court-sex-consent-age-teen-romance-pocso-act-age-of-marriage-232693%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Eobserved%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhilst%20all%20children%20are%20entitled%20to%20be%20protected%20from%20sexual%20violence%2C%20such%20protection%20should%20also%20enable%20young%20people%20to%20extend%20their%20boundaries%2C%20exercise%20choices%20and%20engage%20in%20necessary%20risk%20taking%20though%20not%20exposing%20them%20to%20inappropriate%20response%2C%20harm%20and%20danger.%20The%20penal%20approach%20towards%20adolescents%E2%80%99%20sexuality%20has%20impacted%20their%20life%20to%20a%20barrier%20free%20access%20to%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Dangre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20made%20these%20observations%20while%20acquitting%20a%20man%20convicted%20under%20the%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20Act%20(POCSO%20Act)%20in%202016%20for%20having%20sexual%20relations%20with%20a%20minor%20girl.%20The%20then%2025-year-old%20man%20and%2017-year-old%20girl%20said%20that%20they%20were%20in%20a%20consensual%20relationship.%20The%20girl%20also%20stated%20that%20she%20was%20an%20adult%20under%20Muslim%20law%20and%20hence%20she%20had%20%3Cem%3ENikah%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marriage)%20with%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trial%20court%20had%20observed%20that%20while%20the%20relationship%20was%20consensual%2C%20the%20girl%20was%20a%20few%20months%20short%20of%20turning%2018%20and%20a%20sexual%20relationship%20with%20her%20would%20amount%20to%20rape%20since%20a%20minor%E2%80%99s%20consent%20is%20immaterial%2C%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fbombay-high-court-sex-consent-age-teen-romance-pocso-act-age-of-marriage-232693%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20evidence%20clearly%20established%20consensual%20sexual%20activity%2C%20and%20the%20conviction%20was%20erroneous.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20citing%20examples%20of%20age%20of%20consent%20in%20various%20countries%2C%20the%20court%20said%20India%20has%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20age%20of%20consent%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livel