%20'Kick'%20is%20one%20of%20his%20favourite%20intellectual%20properties%20and%20the%20subject%20is%20there%20on%20paper%20but%20needs%20time.%20He%20further%20added%20that%20they%20need%20a%20bigger%20scale%20and%20a%20better%20time%20for%20the%20release%20of%20the%20movie.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsajid-nadiadwala-reveals-script-of-salman-khan-and-jacqueline-fernandez-starrer-kick-2-is-ready-deets-inside%2Farticleshow%2F101747809.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Hollywood%20Is%20On%20Strike%20And%20What%20It%20Means%20For%20Actors%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20second%20time%20in%20film%20history%2C%20two%20Hollywood%20unions%20have%20gone%20on%20strike%2C%20shutting%20down%20production%20on%20current%20and%20future%20projects.%20Actors%20joined%20Hollywood's%20writers%20on%20picket%20lines%20today.%20The%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20announced%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20strike%20would%20be%20effective%20midnight%2C%20prompting%20the%20cast%20of%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20leave%20the%20film's%20London%20premiere.%C2%A0%20The%20last%20time%20both%20unions%20went%20on%20strike%20together%20was%20in%201960%20%E2%80%93%20actors%20and%20writers%20have%20picketed%20separately%20at%20other%20times.%20Here's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20the%20big%20Hollywood%20shut%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHY%20HOLLYWOOD%20IS%20ON%20STRIKE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Screen%20Actors%20Guild%20and%20Writers%20Guild%20are%20asking%20for%20better%20pay%2C%20a%20fair%20share%20of%20profits%2C%20improved%20working%20conditions%20and%20protection%20against%20artificial%20intelligence%20or%20AI%20taking%20their%20jobs.%20SAG%20has%20also%20asked%20for%20actors%20sending%20in%20self-made%20auditions%20to%20be%20compensated.%20On%20a%20website%20created%20for%20the%20strike%2C%20SAG%20says%20it%20wants%20%26quot%3Ba%20modern%20contract%C2%A0%20that%20addresses%20modern%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20big%20concern%20for%20both%20actors%20and%20writers%20is%20the%20drop%20in%20payments%20known%20as%20residuals%20%E2%80%93%20these%20are%20payments%20received%20by%20performers%20from%20re-runs%20of%20their%20films%20and%20shows.%20Residuals%20have%20all%20but%20disappeared%20because%20streaming%20sites%20do%20not%20disclose%20their%20audience%20figures%20and%20pay%20a%20flat%20rate%20as%20residuals%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHO%20THEY%20ARE%20STRIKING%20AGAINST%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guilds%20are%20striking%20against%20the%20AMPTP%20or%20Alliance%20Of%20Motion%20Picture%20And%20Television%20Producers%2C%20which%20includes%20the%20major%20Hollywood%20studios.%20SAG%20extended%20their%20deadline%20for%20a%20strike%20%E2%80%93%20set%20for%20a%20month%20ago%20%E2%80%93%20in%20hopes%20of%20a%20deal%20with%20studios.%20%26quot%3BWe%2C%20in%20good%20faith%2C%20gave%20them%20an%20extension%2C%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20they%20would%20make%20deep%20inroads%2C%20and%20we%20would%20really%20have%20something%20to%20discuss.%20But%20we%20were%20duped.%20They%20stayed%20behind%20closed%20doors%2C%20they%20kept%20canceling%20our%20meetings%2C%20wasting%20time.%20It%20was%20probably%20all%20to%20have%20more%20time%20to%20promote%20their%20summer%20movies.%20Because%20nothing%20came%20out%20of%20it%20that%20was%20significant%2C%26quot%3B%20SAG%20president%20Fran%20Descher%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHad%20the%20strike%20begun%20a%20month%20ago%2C%20actors%20like%20Tom%20Cruise%2C%20Margot%20Robbie%20and%20Ryan%20Gosling%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20promote%20their%20movies%20%3Cem%3EMission%3A%20Impossible%20%E2%80%93%20Dead%20Reckoning%20Part%20One%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EBarbie%3C%2Fem%3E%20(which%20held%20a%20premiere%20earlier%20this%20week).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20ACTORS%20CANNOT%20DO%20WHILE%20ON%20STRIKE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG%20represents%20some%201%2C60%2C000%20artistes%20including%20most%20of%20Hollywood's%20top%20stars.%20While%20on%20strike%2C%20SAG%20members%20cannot%20do%20any%20on%20or%20off%20camera%20work%20including%20acting%2C%20dancing%2C%20singing%20or%20voice%20acting.%20They%20cannot%20promote%20their%20films%20or%20attend%20premieres%2C%20festivals%2C%20panels%2C%20interviews%2C%20award%20shows%20or%20fan%20meets.%20They%20cannot%20rehearse%20or%20attend%20costume%20fittings.%20They%20can%20also%20not%20negotiate%20for%20future%20projects.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActors%20will%20picket%20studios%20like%20Netflix%2C%20Disney%2C%20Warner%20Bros%20and%20Paramount%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20and%20New%20York%2C%20joining%20writers%20who%20have%20been%20picketing%20since%20May%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%225jadqpuk%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F5jadqpuk_oppenheimerembed_625x300_14_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3ECillian%20Murphy%2C%20Emily%20Blunt%2C%20Matt%20Damon%20and%20Florence%20Pugh%20before%20leaving%20the%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%20%3C%2Fem%3Epremiere%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOW%20THE%20STRIKE%20WILL%20IMPACT%20HOLLYWOOD%20FILMS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirector%20Christopher%20Nolan's%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20the%20first%20to%20feel%20the%20blow%20with%20the%20film's%20cast%2C%20led%20by%20actors%20Cillian%20Murphy%20and%20Emily%20Blunt%2C%20walking%20out%20of%20the%20premiere%20in%20London.%20The%20premiere%20for%20%3Cem%3ESpecial%20Ops%3A%20Lioness%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20starring%20Nicole%20Kidman%2C%20Zoe%20Saldana%2C%20Morgan%20Freeman%20and%20others%2C%20has%20been%20cancelled%20and%20more%20cancellations%20are%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20week's%20'Barbenheimer'%20clash%20between%