n-latest-share-market-updates-123071400107_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stock%20market%20live%20on%20July%2014%2C%202023%3A%20JBM%20Auto%20surged%2014%20per%20cent%20on%20winning%20orders%20for%205%2C000%20electric%20buses%20for%20supplying%20to%20various%20STUs%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-july-14-sensex-nifty-gift-nse-bse-wipro-senco-gold-wpi-inflation-latest-share-market-updates-123071400107_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-july-14-sensex-nifty-gift-nse-bse-wipro-senco-gold-wpi-inflation-latest-share-market-updates-123071400107_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-july-14-sensex-nifty-gift-nse-bse-wipro-senco-gold-wpi-inflation-latest-share-market-updates-123071400107_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIMs%20Oppose%20Union%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Diktat%20to%20Translate%20Syllabus%20Into%20Local%20Languages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14094307%2FIIMB_entrance.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20education%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20diktat%20to%20translate%20existing%20teaching%20material%20into%20local%20languages%20has%20been%20ignored%20by%20as%20many%20as%2017%20IIMs%20and%20refused%20by%20three%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fedugraph%2Fiims-snub-union-ministry-over-diktat-on-translation-of-existing-literature%2Fcid%2F1951905%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20issued%20an%20office%20memorandum%20in%20October%202021%20with%20the%20subject%20line%3A%20%E2%80%9CAzadi%20Ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%20%E2%80%94%20Translation%20of%20existing%20literature%20by%20Universities%20(using%20AICTE%20translation%20tools)%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20as%20part%20of%20an%20initiative%20to%20offer%20professional%20courses%20in%20local%20languages%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20has%20been%20decided%20that%20under%20Azadi%20Ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav%2C%20existing%20literature%20has%20to%20be%20translated%20in%20different%20Indian%20languages.%20At%20least%2075%20Universities%20have%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20this%20activity%20over%20next%20two%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20documents%20accessed%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUGC%20(the%20University%20Grants%20Commission)%20and%20Bureau%20Heads%20are%20requested%20to%20mobilise%20Universities%2FAutonomous%20Organisations%2C%20under%20their%20administrative%20control%2C%20in%20this%20exercise%20and%20keep%20this%20Division%20informed%20of%20the%20activities%20being%20taken%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20office%20memorandum%20was%20forwarded%20to%20all%20institutions%2C%20including%20the%20IIMs%2C%20under%20the%20ministry%20in%20November%202021%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20IIM%20Bangalore%2C%20IIM%20Kashipur%20and%20IIM%20Udaipur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fedugraph%2Fiims-snub-union-ministry-over-diktat-on-translation-of-existing-literature%2Fcid%2F1951905%5C%22%3Ewrote%20back%3C%2Fa%3E%20saying%20that%20the%20order%20was%20not%20applicable%20to%20them%2C%20the%20remaining%2017%20have%20not%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIIMB%20is%20a%20Management%20Institute.%20We%20do%20not%20have%20literature%20for%20translation%20into%20other%20languages%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20the%20chief%20administrative%20officer%20of%20IIM%20Bangalore%20in%20an%20email%20to%20the%20Union%20education%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIM%20Udaipur%E2%80%99s%20then%20director%2C%20Janat%20Shah%2C%20wrote%20back%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20like%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20translation%20of%20existing%20literature%20by%20Universities%20(using%20AICTE%20translation%20tools)%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20IIM%20Udaipur.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIM%20Kashipur%20chief%20administrative%20officer%20M.%20Ramasubramanian%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CWith%20respect%20to%20the%20training%20email%2C%20this%20is%20to%20inform%20you%20that%20the%20matter%20is%20not%20applicable%20to%20IIM%20Kashipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Council%20for%20Technical%20Education%20(AICTE)%20is%20using%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20translate%20literature%20in%20existing%20subjects%20to%20local%20languages%20as%20IITs%20and%20NITs%20are%20also%20being%20persuaded%20to%20offer%20their%20courses%20in%20Indian%20languages%20under%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689309057000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F14094307%2FIIMB_entrance.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiims-oppose-union-governments-diktat-to-translate-syllabus-into-local-languages%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20education%20ministry%20had%20issued%20an%20office%20memorandum%20in%202021%20asking%20at%20least%2075%20institutions%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20exercise%20as%20part%20of%20'Azadi%20Ka%20Amrit%20Mahotsav'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiims-oppose-union-governments-diktat-to-translate-syllabus-into-local-languages%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20is%20egging%20Southeast%20Asian%20countries%20to%20ditch%20the%20dollar%20to%20get%20around%20Western%20sanctions%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20shows%20just%20how%20desperately%20it%20wants%20to%20save%20its%20fla