are%20now%20at%20a%20India-France%20ties%20strong%2C%20look%20forward%20to%20roadmap%20for%20next%2025%20years%3A%20PM%20turning%20point.%20If%20we%20look%20at%20the%20post-pandemic%20global%20order%20and%20the%20shape%20that%20it%20is%20taking%2C%20I%20think%20the%20positive%20experience%20of%20our%20strategic%20partnership%20is%20an%20important%20step%20ahead.%20So%2C%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20working%20on%20a%20roadmap%20for%20the%20next%2025%20years%20of%20the%20strategic%20partnership%2C%20which%20I%20think%20is%20very%20important%20for%20the%20relationship.%20The%20relationship%20is%20in%20excellent%20shape.%20It%20is%20strong%2C%20trusted%2C%20consistent.%20It%20has%20been%20steady%20and%20resilient%20in%20the%20darkest%20storms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20the%20French%20newspaper%20%3Cem%3ELes%20Echos%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fexplainer-pm-modi-france-visit-defence-military-ties%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20will%20be%20dominated%20by%20the%20spectacle%20of%20Indian%20soldiers%20taking%20part%20in%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20military%20parades%20in%20Europe%2C%20which%20will%20again%20underline%20that%20defence%20cooperation%20remains%20a%20mainstay%20of%20bilateral%20ties%20with%20announcements%20of%20new%20deals%20on%20engines%2C%20submarines%20and%20fighter%20jets%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20Read%20more%20on%20what%20to%20expect%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fexplainer-pm-modi-france-visit-defence-military-ties%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECriticism%20for%20invitation%20to%20Modi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20in%20France%20who%20have%20criticised%20Macron%20for%20extending%20an%20invite%20to%20Modi%20despite%20his%20questionable%20human%20rights%20record%20in%20India.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20friend.%20But%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20M