ives%20foreign%20minister%20Abdulla%20Shahid%20admitted%20that%20it%20would%20have%20been%20far%20%E2%80%9Csimpler%E2%80%9D%20if%20the%20ruling%20party%20had%20remained%20intact%20and%20the%20coalition%20had%20retained%20its%20original%20composition.%20But%20he%20claimed%20that%20with%20opposition%20members%20also%20joining%20the%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%20(MDP)%2C%20it%20would%20also%20get%20new%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaldives%20will%20be%20holding%20its%20presidential%20elections%20on%20September%209.%20If%20none%20of%20the%20candidates%20win%2050%25%20of%20the%20votes%2C%20then%20a%20run-off%20will%20be%20held%20within%2021%20days.%20In%20the%202018%20elections%2C%20Ibrahim%20Solih%2C%20the%20candidate%20of%20a%20united%20opposition%2C%20won%20a%20surprise%20victory%20over%20President%20Abdulla%20Yameen%20with%2058%25%20of%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20electoral%20fray%20is%20much%20more%20fractious%2C%20with%20three%20presidential%20candidates%20already%20announced%20and%20two%20more%20likely%20to%20jump%20in%20soon.%20The%20picture%20will%20be%20clearer%20once%20the%20nominations%20open%20on%20July%2023%20and%20the%20high%20court%20gives%20an%20order%20on%20the%20appeal%20by%20former%20President%20Yameen%20on%20his%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20heightened%20political%20temperature%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20island%20nation%2C%20Shahid%20was%20in%20New%20Delhi%20for%20three%20days%20during%20which%20he%20met%20with%20his%20Indian%20counterpart%20and%20also%20met%20with%20other%20members%20of%20the%20diplomatic%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20about%20the%20outcome%20of%20his%20visit%2C%20the%20domestic%20political%20outlook%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20opposition%20criticism%20over%20the%20Maldives%20government%E2%80%99s%20revised%20stance%20on%20Chagos%2C%20and%20whether%20relations%20with%20India%20will%20be%20an%20electoral%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transcript%20below%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20brings%20you%20back%20to%20India%20right%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20last%20visit%2C%20I%20was%20here%20as%20the%20president%20of%20the%20General%20Assembly%2C%20but%20this%20visit%20is%20on%20bilateral%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20that%20marks%20the%20relationship%20between%20our%20two%20countries%20during%20this%20presidency%20of%20President%20(Ibrahim)%20Solih%20is%20the%20frequency%20of%20high%20level%20visits.%20I%20think%20I%20have%20been%20to%20Delhi%20in%20my%20capacity%20as%20foreign%20minister%20five%20to%20six%20times%20during%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20And%20the%20EAM%20%5BIndian%20external%20affairs%20minister%5D%20also%20has%20visited%20Maldives%20a%20number%20of%20times.%20Most%20recently%2C%20the%20%5BIndian%5D%20defence%20minister%20was%20in%20Maldives.%20Also%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20%5Bfor%20external%20affairs%5D%20was%20there.%20The%20prime%20minister%20%5Bof%20India%5D%20visited%20Maldives%20twice.%20President%20Solih%20has%20been%20here%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20level%20visits%20provides%20opportunity%20to%20consolidate%20and%20put%20our%20officers%2C%20who%20are%20supposed%20to%20implement%20what%20we%20agreed%20upon%2C%20to%20task%20when%20we%20sit%20down%20and%20review%20what%20progress%20has%20been%20made%20on%20a%20regular%20basis.%20Then%20we%20are%20able%20to%20push%20for%20continued%20progress%20on%20what%20we%20agreed.%20Otherwise%20very%20often%2C%20we%20start%20things%20and%20then%20we%20lose%20focus%20as%20we%20move%20on%20to%20other%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20progressed%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years%20because%20at%20the%20very%20highest%20level%2C%20the%20level%20of%20the%20president%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20they%20sit%20down%20and%20review%20what%20is%20going%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20during%20this%20visit%2C%20the%20EAM%20and%20I%20have%20done%20the%20same.%20We%20have%20reviewed%20the%20progress%20of%20what%20is%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20also%20we%20have%20signed%20and%20exchanged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.mv%2Fen%2Fnews-and-communications%2Fceremony-held-to-exchange-memorandums-of-understanding-between-maldives-and-india-11-07-2023%5C%22%3Enine%20MoUs%20on%20high%20impact%20community%20development%20projects%3C%2Fa%3E%20ranging%20from%20small%20fish%20processing%20plants%20to%20street%20lighting%2C%20to%20volleyball%20courts%20and%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20was%20the%20assessment%20of%20the%20speed%20of%20implementation%20of%20the%20projects%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20them%20are%20on%20track.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20which%20are%20slightly%20behind.%20So%20both%20of%20us%20meeting%20at%20this%20level%20gives%20the%20task%20to%20our%20officers%20to%20do%20regular%20follow%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20any%20specific%20projects%20which%20require%20greater%20momentum%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-maldives-launch-greater-male-connectivity-projects-india-extends-100-million-line-of-credit%2Farticleshow%2F93294827.cms%5C%22%3EGreater%20Male%20connectivity%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20slightly%20behind%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20what%20are%20the%20reasons%20for%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20tasked%20the%20relevant%20teams%20to%20take%20necessary%20steps%20to%20push%20forward%E2%80%A6%20There%20were%20unforeseen%20circumstances%20%5Bleading%20to%20the%20delay%5D%2C%20contractual%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20a%20flagship%20project%20for%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20and%20for%20the%20Maldives%20as%20well.%20It%E2%80%99s%20going%20well%2C%20but%20slightly%20behind%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20could%20be%20some%20criticism%20that%20the%20nine%20MoUs%20for%20community%20development%20projects%20were%20signed%20too%20close%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20less%20than%20two%20months%20away.%20How%20would%20you%20react%20to%20that%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20link%20everything%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20The%20people%20of%20Dhiggaru%2C%20who%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20this%20fish%20processing%20plant%2C%20why%20should%20they%20be%20denied%20the%20plant%20that%20they%20have%20been%20wanting%20for%20so%20long%3F%20Why%20should%20the%20youth%20of%20Kanditheemu%20be%20denied%20the%20volley%20court%20that%20they%20have%20been%20desiring%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20means%20are%20available%2C%20then%20we%20should%20go%20ahead%20with%20it%20because%20even%20with%20elections%2C%20the%20country%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20come%20to%20a%20stop.%20The%20country%20continues%20to%20function%2C%20the%20government%20continues%20to%20function%20and%20we%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20say%2C%20well%2C%20it%20is%20election%20time%20and%20we%20are%20stopping%20everything.%20That%20is%20not%20the%20spirit%20of%20elections.%20We%20were%20elected%20for%20a%20five-year%20term%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20deliver%20until%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20five-year%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20major%20leader%20of%20your%20party%20left%20and%20has%20formed%20a%20new%20political%20party.%20Former%20President%20Nasheed%20has%20also%20indicated%20a%20willingness%20to%20work%20with%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20led%20by%20former%20president%20Abdulla%20Yameen.%20How%20do%20you%20look%20at%20the%20electoral%20scenario%20against%20this%20backdrop%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20leader%20left%2C%20but%20the%20MDP%20is%20intact%20and%20solidly%20behind%20the%20candidate%20who%20won%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fmaldives-president-solih-wins-presidential-primary-party-says-2023-01-29%2F%5C%22%3Einternal%20primaries%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20was%20President%20Solih.%20He%20had%20the%20backing%20of%2061%25%20of%20the%20voters%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20internal%20primary.%20So%20that%20very%20clearly%20said%20that%20he%20is%20the%20person%20behind%20whom%20MDP%20will%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20have%20a%20coalition%20with%20the%20Adhalaath%20party%2C%20one%20of%20our%20old%20partners%2C%20and%20also%20with%20the%20MDA%20headed%20by%20Ahmed%20Shiyam.%20Together%2C%20this%20coalition%20today%20has%20total%20membership%20of%20over%2077%2C000.%20Membership%20wise%2C%20this%20is%20the%20largest%20coalition%20that%20the%20country%20has%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20if%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2F2023%2F07%2Fformer-adversaries-unite-to-challenge-president-solih-in-maldives-presidential-elections%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPresident%20Nasheed%20is%20joining%20hands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20with%20the%20PPM%20and%20Jumhoree%20Party%20has%20its%20own%20platform%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20that%20a%20setback%20for%20the%20ruling%20coalition%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20election%20would%20have%20been%20very%20simple%20if%20President%20Nasheed%20had%20not%20left%20the%20party.%20It%20would%20have%20been%20simpler%20if%20the%20current%20coalition%20including%20the%20Jumhoree%20Party%20stuck%20together.%20But%20that%20is%20not%20the%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJumhoree%20Party%20leader%20Gasim%20Ibrahim%20has%20very%20clearly%20announced%20his%20presidential%20ambition.%20He%20has%20been%20awarded%20the%20candidacy%20by%20his%20own%20party.%20So%20it%20looks%20like%20that%20he%20will%20contest%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWon%E2%80%99t%20this%20splinter%20the%20votes%20that%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20had%20got%20in%20the%20last%20presidential%20election%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20last%20two%20months%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20not%20only%20members%20from%20the%20MDP%20leave%20MDP%20and%20form%20other%20parties%2C%20but%20members%20from%20other%20parties%20like%20JP%20and%20MRM%20have%20joined%20MDP.%20From%20PPM%2C%20several%20councillors%20have%20joined%20us%20and%20with%20them%2C%20we%20will%20get%20PPM%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20parliament%20%E2%80%93%20yes%2C%2013%20of%20our%20members%20left%20and%20joined%20the%20newly%20formed%20The%20Democrats.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20also%20have%20MPs%20from%20other%20parties%20come%20and%20join%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20election%20commissioner%20has%20said%20he%20has%20no%20objection%20to%20President%20Yameen%20submitting%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.mv%2Feu%2F28383%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ehis%20form%20for%20candidacy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20Do%20you%20expect%20him%20to%20be%20a%20presidential%20candidate%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20unfair%20for%20me%20to%20say%20something%20on%20it%20because%20it%20will%20be%20for%20the%20elections%20commission%20and%20the%20judiciary%20to%20decide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20India%20figure%20during%20the%20campaigning%20as%20an%20electoral%20issue%3F%20President%20Solih%20is%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20Indian%20government.%20Is%20that%20something%20that%20you%20expect%20to%20defend%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20between%20Maldives%20and%20India%20is%20not%20between%20governments.%20It%E2%80%99s%20between%20the%20people%20of%20the%20two%20countries.%20So%20the%20few%20individuals%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20create%20hatred%20between%20our%20two%20peoples%2C%20they%20are%20not%20going%20to%20succeed.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20efforts%20by%20PPM%20to%20have%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fasia-pacific%2Fmaldives-former-president-plots-comeback-with-india-out-campaign-2022-03-25%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98India%20Out%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%98%20campaign%20has%20not%20really%20taken%20off.%20It%E2%80%99s%20always%20on%20the%20fringe%2C%20just%20led%20by%20President%20Yameen%20and%20his%20team.%20But%20nationwide%2C%20there%20has%20no%20support%20for%20it%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20they%20have%20not%20given%20up%20on%20the%20campaign.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20they%20have%20nothing%20else%20to%20say.%20They%20have%20nothing%20else%20to%20sell.%20Nothing.%20No%20solid%20policies.%20No%20developmental%20plans%2C%20no%20economic%20policies%2C%20nothing.%20And%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20it%2C%20all%20they%20can%20sell%20is%20hatred%20and%20that%20is%20what%20they%20are%20doing.%20Ultra-nationalism%20is%20what%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20you%20look%20at%20the%20history%20of%20cooperation%20between%20our%20two%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20look%20at%201988%20the%20mercenary%20attack%20and%202004%20tsunami%2C%20both%20times%20when%20India%20was%20the%20first%20responder.%20President%20Gayoom%20was%20in%20office%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELook%20at%20the%20Male%20water%20crisis%20in%202015.%20It%20was%20President%20Yameen%20in%20office.%20Within%20six%20hours%20of%20Male%20running%20out%20of%20drinking%20water%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhci.gov.in%2Fmale%2F%3F3840%3F00%5C%22%3EIndia%20airlifted%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20residents.%20It%20was%20Yameen%E2%80%99s%20government%20then.%20During%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20when%20President%20Solih%C2%A0was%20in%20office%2C%20India%20came%20to%20our%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20irrespective%20of%20who%20is%20in%20office%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20been%20most%20generous.%20Again%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20government%20in%20Male%20or%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20trying%20to%20create%20hatred%20between%20our%20two%20peoples%20is%20something%20that%20will%20not%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20you%20expect%20the%20Chagos%20issue%20to%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fatolltimes.mv%2Fpost%2Fnews%2F3725%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eflare%20up%20politically%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20like%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20again%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20nothing%20to%20stand%20on%2C%20there%20is%20no%20solid%20platform%20of%20policies%20for%20them.%20They%20were%20trying%20to%20cling%20on%20to%20anything%2C%20anything%20just%20to%20keep%20them%20afloat.%20So%20yes%2C%20that%20was%20something%20they%20tried%20to%20create%20a%20huge%20brouhaha%20about.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20long%20as%20we%20are%20party%20to%20the%20law%20of%20the%20Sea%20Convention%20%5BUNCLOS%5D%20and%20other%20international%20conventions%20and%20agreements%20and%20as%20long%20as%20we%20respect%20an%20international%20rules-based%20system%2C%20we%E2%80%99ll%20have%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.itlos.org%2Fen%2Fmain%2Fcases%2Flist-of-cases%2Fdispute-concerning-delimitation-of-the-maritime-boundary-between-mauritius-and-maldives-in-the-indian-ocean-mauritius%2Fmaldives%2F%5C%22%3EITLOS%20ruling%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Also%20it%E2%80%99s%20clearly%20given%20in%20the%20ruling%20that%20Maldives%20got%20most%20of%20the%20territorial%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20the%20court%20had%20also%20disregarded%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20contention%20that%20ITLOS%20had%20no%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20our%20first%20defence%20that%20ITLOS%20does%20not%20have%20the%20jurisdiction%20or%20Mauritius%20does%20not%20have%20the%20right%20to%20contest%20at%20ITLOS.%20It%20ruled%20that%20the%20Mauritius%20has%20the%20right%20because%20of%20the%20ICJ%20advisory%20opinion%20and%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20resolution%20which%20was%20adopted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%