ary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Asian%20states%20need%20to%20have%20good%20relations%20for%20playing%20an%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%20role%20in%20the%20new%20multipolar%20world%20order%2C%20as%20the%20only%20way%20for%20the%20West%20in%20its%20endeavours%20for%20hegemony%20is%20to%20create%20conflicts%20among%20the%20world%20countries%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20ministerial%20visit%20to%20the%20West%20Asian%20country%20since%202018%20and%20comes%20after%20Syrian%20foreign%20minister%20Fayssal%20Mekdad%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20Delhi%20last%20year.%20He%20held%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Findia-assures-to-continue-humanitarian-assistance-to-syria%2F1224519%2F%5C%22%3Emeeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20external%20affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20assured%20continued%20humanitarian%20support%20to%20the%20country%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20Assad%20government%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Syria%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F5%2F7%2Farab-league-agrees-to-bring-syria-back-into-its-fold%5C%22%3Eregaining%20its%20membership%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Arab%20League%20in%20May%20this%20year.%20Its%20membership%20was%20revoked%20after%20al-Assad%20ordered%20a%20crackdown%20on%20pro-democracy%20protesters%20during%20the%20so-called%20Arab%20Spring%20in%20March%202011%2C%20which%20spiralled%20into%20a%20civil%20war%20that%20has%20killed%20nearly%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20and%20displaced%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20conflict%2C%20India%20did%20not%20criticise%20the%20government%20and%20remained%20aligned%20with%20al-Assad.%20New%20Delhi%20also%20continued%20economic%20involvement%20in%20Syria.%20India%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icwa.in%2Fshow_content.php%3Flang%3D1%26level%3D3%26ls_id%3D2387%26lid%3D1787%26kval%3Dsyria%5C%22%3Eopposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20external%20intervention%20or%20imposed%20solutions%20to%20the%20conflict%20and%20instead%20proposed%20a%20%E2%80%9CSyria-led%20solution%20in%20Syria%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Funsc-watch-as-russia-us-clash-over-syria-cross-border-aid-india-aligns-with-moscow%5C%22%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20consistent%20support%20for%20the%20al-Assad%20regime%20is%20principally%20based%20on%20its%20assessment%20that%20he%20had%20been%20an%20%E2%80%9Ceffective%20bulwark%20against%20the%20spread%20of%20the%20terror%20group%20ISIS%2C%20not%20only%20in%20West%20Asia%20but%20also%20in%20the%20larger%20region%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689261364000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13203458%2FF06z2U-XgAIzlT-.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmuraleedharan-meets-syrian-president-bashar-al-assad%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Syrian%20president%20described%20the%20relations%20binding%20the%20two%20countries%20as%20%26quot%3Bdeep-rooted%26quot%3B%20and%20hailed%20India%E2%80%99s%20%26quot%3Bfirm%20objective%20stances%20on%20Arab%20issues%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20its%20stances%20towards%20the%20war%20waged%20against%20Syria%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmuraleedharan-meets-syrian-president-bashar-al-assad%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20PM%20Sharif%20will%20hand%20over%20power%20to%20caretaker%20govt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689260599000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101734611%2Cimgsize-1184233.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fpakistan-pm-shehbaz-sharif-will-hand-over-power-to-caretaker-government%2Farticleshow