20the%20Kiran%20Nadar%20Museum%20of%20Art%20(KNMA)%2C%20who%20was%20%E2%80%9Carbitrarily%E2%80%9D%20fired%20for%20a%20Facebook%20post%20that%20was%20critical%20of%20the%20museum%E2%80%99s%20chairperson%20and%20namesake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELuis%20had%20criticised%20Kiran%20Nadar%20for%20supporting%20and%20endorsing%20a%20series%20of%20events%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20showcasing%20at%20the%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20(NGMA)%20in%20Delhi%20%E2%80%93%20events%20that%20many%20in%20the%20art%20world%20have%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cself-aggrandizing%20exercise%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20in%20support%20of%20Luis%2C%20the%20artists%20and%20others%20said%20that%20dismissing%20a%20museum%20employee%20for%20a%20social%20media%20post%20made%20in%20his%20individual%20capacity%20%E2%80%9Cpoints%20to%20a%20high-handed%20way%20of%20functioning%20that%20does%20not%20recognize%20the%20constitutionally%20enshrined%20right%20to%20free%20speech.%20The%20art%20world%20requires%20critically%20informed%20voices%20to%20be%20given%20the%20space%20to%20express%20concerns%20that%20will%20shape%20its%20future%20in%20a%20constructive%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20the%20undersigned%2C%20artists%2C%20academics%20and%20other%20concerned%20individuals%2C%20have%20come%20to%20know%20that%20Dr%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%2C%20Manager%2C%20Curatorial%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Publications%20at%20the%20Kiran%20Nadar%20Museum%20of%20Art%20(KNMA)%2C%20has%20arbitrarily%20been%20terminated%20from%20work.%20The%20action%20was%20taken%20for%20a%20Facebook%20post%20he%20made%20on%2015th%20May%202023%20which%20was%20critical%20of%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20museum%20Ms.%20Kiran%20Nadar%20in%20her%20individual%20capacity%2C%20for%20supporting%20and%20publicly%20endorsing%20a%20series%20of%20propaganda%20events%20of%20the%20current%20government%20of%20India%20being%20showcased%20at%20the%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20(NGMA)%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Facebook%20post%20was%20also%20published%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkafila.online%2F2023%2F05%2F17%2Fdecoding-jan-shakti-at-national-gallery-of-modern-art-there-is-no-schindlers-list-sandip-k-luis%2F%5C%22%3EDecoding%20Jan%20Shakti%20at%20National%20Gallery%20of%20Modern%20Art%20-there%20is%20no%20Schindler%E2%80%99s%20List!%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20strongly%20condemn%20Sandip%E2%80%99s%20termination%20from%20employment%20and%20demand%20his%20immediate%20reinstatement%20by%20KNMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequent%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20an%20exhibition%20in%20May%202023%2C%20titled%20Jana%20Shakti%20(a%20celebration%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20monthly%20radio%20propaganda%20Mann%20ki%20baat)%20curated%20by%20Alka%20Pande%2C%20supported%20by%20Ms.%20Nadar%20as%20the%20Advisor%2C%20a%20number%20of%20articles%20appeared%20in%20the%20press%20and%20on%20social%20media%20that%20called%20out%20art%20world%20luminaries%2C%20for%20participating%20in%20what%20was%20obviously%20a%20self-aggrandizing%20exercise%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India.%20The%20exhibition%20in%20effect%20had%20instrumentalized%20artists%20and%20artworks%20to%20obfuscate%20ground%20realities%20of%20our%20times.%20Sandip%20in%20his%20capacity%20as%20an%20academic%2C%20contributed%20to%20this%20discussion%20through%20his%20social%20media%20post%2C%20not%20as%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20museum%2C%20but%20as%20a%20thinking%20individual%20who%20recognized%20the%20systems%20of%20domination%20and%20exploitation%20that%20marked%20the%20emerging%20order%20of%20private%20wealth%20and%20its%20role%20in%20constructing%20false%20narratives%20of%20art%20and%20politics%20around.%20In%20response%2C%20he%20was%20served%20a%20%E2%80%9Cshow%20cause%E2%80%9D%20notice%20and%20then%20subsequently%20terminated%20from%20employment%20in%20a%20highly%20opaque%20manner%20by%20the%20museum%20where%20he%20was%20employed%3B%20a%20museum%20that%20is%20supported%20by%20the%20Shiv%20Nadar%20Foundation%2C%20the%20Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility%20arm%20of%20HCL%20Tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20odd%20that%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20KNMA%2C%20a%20museum%20renowned%20for%20its%20collection%20of%20critically%20acclaimed%20art%20works%20and%20curated%20shows%2C%20was%20not%20able%20to%20accept%20criticism%20of%20her%20own%20shortcomings.%20Mrs.%20Nadar%E2%80%99s%20support%20of%20a%20regressive%20propagandist%20event%20seems%20to%20indicate%20her%20inability%20to%20understand%20the%20critical%20function%20of%20art%20in%20the%20present%20political%20climate%2C%20and%20her%20lack%20of%20subject%20expertise%20to%20shape%20art%20exhibitions%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20point%20out%20that%20the%20cultural%20capital%20accrued%20by%20Mrs%20Nadar%20is%20the%20result%20of%20hard%20work%20put%20in%20by%20many%20individuals%20who%20work%20behind%20the%20scenes%20of%20the%20institution%20that%20carries%20her%20name%2C%20the%20Kiran%20Nadar%20Museum%20of%20Art.%20They%20bring%20to%20bear%20their%20academic%20training%20in%20identifying%20important%20strands%20of%20thinking%2C%20significance%20of%20artworks%20and%20advise%20her%20on%20how%20to%20build%20a%20historically%20relevant%20art%20collection.%20Curation%20requires%20depth%20of%20knowledge%2C%20theorizing%20and%20narrativizing%20for%20public%20access%20and%20knowledge%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20when%20we%E2%80%99re%20locked%20in%20a%20crisis%20where%20government%20run%20cultural%20institutions%20have%20become%20instruments%20of%20state%20sponsored%20propaganda%20rather%20than%20spaces%20for%20critical%20thinking%2C%20it%20becomes%20even%20more%20important%20that%20those%20who%20have%20the%20power%20to%20support%20a%20thriving%20artworld%2C%20understand%20its%20transformative%20power%20rather%20than%20seeing%20art%20as%20just%20another%20aspect%20of%20conducting%20business%20as%20usual.%20We%20therefore%20expect%20even%20private%20museums%20to%20function%20as%20forms%20of%20public%20good%20rather%20than%20personal%20fiefdoms%20of%20the%20wealthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20dismiss%20a%20museum%20employee%20for%20a%20social%20media%20post%20made%20in%20his%20individual%20capacity%20points%20to%20a%20high-handed%20way%20of%20functioning%20that%20does%20not%20recognize%20the%20constitutionally%20enshrined%20right%20to%20free%20speech.%20The%20artworld%20requires%20critically%20informed%20voices%20to%20be%20given%20the%20space%20to%20express%20concerns%20that%20will%20shape%20its%20future%20in%20a%20constructive%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20we%20undersigned%20demand%20the%20reinstatement%20of%20Dr%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%20on%20the%20post%20that%20he%20held%20before%20(Manager%2C%20Curatorial%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Publications)%20with%20immediate%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F658855165%2FSupport-to-Sandip-K-Luis%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20Support%20to%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3ESupport%20to%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fuser%2F286754081%2FThe-Wire%23from_embed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20The%20Wire's%20profile%20on%20Scribd%5C%22%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Scribd%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fembeds%2F658855165%2Fcontent%3Fstart_page%3D1%26view_mode%3Dscroll%26access_key%3Dkey-E7nesgMQkYQYEjguk4cD%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20data-auto-height%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20data-aspect-ratio%3D%5C%221.3323485967503692%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Support%20to%20Sandip%20K.%20Luis%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689259194000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%