tml%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fakasa-air-flies-past-spicejet-for-the-first-time-in-domestic-traffic-123071300857_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fakasa-air-flies-past-spicejet-for-the-first-time-in-domestic-traffic-123071300857_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vyapam%202.0%3F%20Allegations%20of%20Recruitment%20Scam%20Resurface%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13192647%2FF0g9YnHagAEuCqI.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhopal%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Employees%20Selection%20Board%20(ESB)%20found%20itself%20in%20controversy%20once%20again%20after%20fresh%20allegations%20of%20large-scale%20rigging%20in%20recruitment%20scams.%20This%20has%20raised%20fears%20that%20the%20ESB%2C%20which%20was%20formerly%20known%20as%20Vyapam%2C%20is%20once%20again%20riddled%20with%20systematic%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20seven%20of%20the%2010%20toppers%20in%20the%20recruitment%20examination%20for%20Group%202%20posts%20like%20patwari%20(a%20revenue%20official)%20are%20from%20a%20nondescript%20examination%20centre%20in%20Gwalior.%20Called%20the%20NRI%20College%20of%20Engineering%20and%20Management%2C%20it%20is%20owned%20by%20BJP%20MLA%20Sanjeev%20Kumar%20Kushwaha%20from%20Bhind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%209.80%20lakh%20candidates%20took%20the%20test%2C%20conducted%20in%20March%20and%20April%20this%20year%20across%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20ESB%20announced%20the%20results%20on%20June%2030%20and%20the%20names%20of%20the%20top%2010%20scorers%20on%20July%2010.%20This%20is%20when%20allegations%20about%20rigging%20emerged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%20that%20conducted%20the%20test%20has%20started%20examining%20CCTV%20footage%20and%20the%20computer%20logs%20of%20the%20centre%20where%20the%20seven%20toppers%20wrote%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20opposition%20parties%20are%20demanding%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FOfficeOfKNath%2Fstatus%2F1679009503768088576%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Eindependent%20probe%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20government%20has%20denied%20any%20irregularities%20in%20the%20recruitment%20test.%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20home%20minister%20and%20government%20spokesperson%20Narottam%20Mishra%20ruled%20out%20any%20irregularities%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20trying%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmislead%E2%80%9D%20people%20ahead%20of%20the%20scheduled%20assembly%20polls%20in%20the%20state%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20nearly%20120%20participants%20have%20cleared%20the%20exam%20at%20that%20particular%20centre.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20are%20questions%20being%20raised%20about%20only%20seven%20toppers%3F%20The%20Congress%20is%20trying%20to%20mislead%20the%20people%20with%20its%20propaganda%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20very%20fact%2C%20former%20Union%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Arun%20Yadav%20says%2C%20is%20suspicious.%20He%20said%20that%20so%20many%20aspirants%20qualifying%20from%20one%20centre%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20past%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20also%20making%20comparisons%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvyapam-scam-mp-elections-bjp-congress%5C%22%3Emulti-layered%20Vyapam%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20rocked%20the%20nation%20exactly%20a%20decade%20ago%20for%20its%20sheer%20magnitude%20and%20macabre%20nature.%20The%20recruitment-cum-examination%20fraud%20that%20surfaced%20in%20July%202013%20involved%20a%20mind-boggling%20number%20of%20politicians%2C%20bureaucrats%2C%20middlemen%2C%20impersonators%20and%20job%20aspirants.%20They%20were%20found%20to%20be%20complicit%20in%20an%20organised%20racket%20that%20manipulated%20in%20myriad%20ways%20the%20processes%20of%20various%20recruitment%20and%20pre-medical%20tests%20conducted%20by%20the%20Professional%20Examination%20Board%20or%20Vyavasayik%20Pariksha%20Mandal%20(Vyapam)%20since%202008%20to%20rake%20in%20the%20moolah.%20Nearly%2045%20persons%20related%20to%20the%20scam%20died%20under%20mysterious%20circumstances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20state%20government%20renamed%20the%20infamous%20Vyapam%20as%20Employees%20Service%20Board%20to%20avoid%20the%20notoriety%20its%20name%20evoked%2C%20allegations%20of%20scams%20in%20the%20recruitments%20conducted%20by%20the%20body%20have%20kept%20surfacing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20Yadav%20alluded%20to%20this%2C%20saying%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThe%20name%20of%20Vyapam%20has%20changed%20thrice%20over%20the%20years.%20But%20the%20corruption%20continues%20unabated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20recruitments%20of%20nursing%20staff%2C%20school%20teachers%2C%20constables%20and%20agriculture%20development%20officers%20have%20attracted%20similar%20allegations%20of%20rigging%20but%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20brazened%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20three%20tests%20%E2%80%93%20agriculture%20extension%20officers%2C%20senior%20agriculture%20officers%20and%20nursing%20staff%20in%202021%20%E2%80%93%20had%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbhopal-news%2F3-mp-recruitment-papers-were-leaked-day-before-test-cancelled-minister-101630088851221.html%5C%22%3Ecancelled%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20government%20because%20the%20scam%20appeared%20too%20glaring%20to%20ignore.%20The%20tests%20were%20mired%20in%20controversy%20after%20marks%20secured%20by%20the%2010%20toppers%20in%20the%20agriculture%20extension%20officers%E2%80%99%20exam%20were%20found%20nearly%20identical%20and%20they%20all%20committed%20the%20same%20errors%20in%20their%20exam.%20Chief%20minister%20Chouhan%20ordered%20an%20inquiry%2C%20which%20showed%20that%20the%20paper%20was%20leaked%20by%20the%20private%20company%20which%20was%20contracted%20to%20conduct%20the%20exams.%20The%20company%20had%20already%20been%20mired%20in%20controversies%20due%20to%20the%20Vyapam%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25143825%2FIMG_3324.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25143825%2FIMG_3324.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25143825%2FIMG_3324-300x120.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F25143825%2FIMG_3324-1024x410.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-488015%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20cries%20foul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20Patwari%20recruitment%20test%20too%2C%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20suspicion%20that%20the%20question%20paper%20may%20have%20been%20leaked.%20Congress%20leader%20Arun%20Yadav%20has%20pointed%20out%20alleged%20inconsistencies%20in%20the%20recruitment%20process.%20Some%20of%20these%2C%20he%20said%2C%20were%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20top%20scorers%20belonged%20to%20a%20minuscule%20fraction%20of%20the%20total%20examinees%2C%20their%20roll%20numbers%20ranging%20from%202488%207991%20to%202488%209693%2C%20from%20a%20pool%20of%20roughly%201%2C700%20candidates.%20Considering%20that%209.8%20lakh%20individuals%20took%20the%20exam%2C%20the%20odds%20of%20such%20a%20coincidence%20are%20highly%20suspicious%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20answer%20sheets%20of%20the%20toppers%20reveal%20that%20they%20signed%20their%20exam%20forms%20in%20Hindi%20but%20answered%20the%20papers%20in%20English.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThese%20candidates%20accurately%20answered%2015%20questions%20which%20were%20later%20cancelled%20by%20the%20ESB%20because%20incorrect%20options%20were%20provided%20as%20answers.%20No%20marks%20were%20awarded%20for%20these%20questions.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20seven%20toppers%20scored%20185%20marks.%20With%20the%20ESB%20removing%2015%20questions%2C%20it%20meant%20that%20the%20candidate%20got%20100%25%20marks.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20body-marking%20column%20(in%20the%20answer%20sheet)%2C%20one%20selected%20candidate%20wrote%20in%20English%3A%20%E2%80%98Cut%20on%20mark%20nose%E2%80%99%3B%20whereas%20the%20correct%20English%20would%20be%20%E2%80%98cut%20mark%20on%20nose%E2%80%99%E2%80%99.%20Arun%20Yadav%20wondered%20how%20she%20got%20100%25%20marks%20in%20English.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20demanded%20a%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20scam%2C%20alleging%20the%20involvement%20of%20BJP%20leaders%20in%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20MLA%20Sanjeev%20Kumar%20Kushwaha%2C%20whose%20college%20in%20Gwalior%20is%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20controversy%2C%20was%20elected%20on%20a%20BSP%20ticket%20but%20later%20joined%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20contacted%2C%20Kushwaha%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20institution%20belongs%20to%20me.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20an%20engineering%20college%2C%20which%20shut%20down%20because%20of%20low%20admissions.%20It%20has%20a%20computer%20lab%20and%20other%20facilities%20which%20are%20now%20used%20as%20a%20test%20centre.%20We%20rent%20out%20the%20place%20for%20conducting%20examinations.%20This%20(patwari)%20examination%20is%20conducted%20by%20the%20Employees%20Selection%20Board%20(ESB)%2C%20you%20should%20ask%20them%20what%20happened.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20stated%20that%20there%20have%20been%20large-scale%20irregularities%20in%20the%20recruitment%20examinations%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CScams%20have%20engulfed%20recruitment%20exams%20such%20as%20nursing%2C%20constable%2C%20agriculture%20extension%20officers%2C%20and%20many%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689256667000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13192647%2FF0g9YnHagAEuCqI.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvyapam-fresh-alelgations-recruitment-scam-madhya-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20has%20raised%20eyebrows%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20seven%20of%20the%2010%20toppers%20in%20the%20recruitment%20examination%20for%20Group%202%20posts%20are%20from%20a%20nondescript%20examination%20centre%20in%20Gwalior.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fvyapam-fresh-alelgations-recruitment-scam-madhya-pradesh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20a%20first%2C%20credit%20card%20spend%20crosses%20Rs%201.4%20trillion-mark%20in%20May%3A%20RBI%20data%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689255967000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2021-07%2F13%2Ffull%2F1626196520-302.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcredit-card-spends-hit-rs-1-4-trillion-in-may-for-the-first-time-rbi-data-123071300844_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Axis%20Bank%2C%20the%20fourth-largest%2C%20is%20closing%20the%20gap%20with%20ICICI%20Bank%20after%20the%20Citi%20acquisition%20with%2012.46%20million%20cards%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcredit-card-spends-hit-rs-1