%2C%20potatoes%20were%20considered%20a%20%3Cem%3Enayab%3C%2Fem%3E%20(exotic)%20delicacy.%20Although%20common%20people%20could%20not%20afford%20them%2C%20the%20vegetable%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20royal%20kitchens.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20it%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20absorb%20all%20aromas%20of%20spices%2C%20it%20enhances%20the%20flavours%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20added%20to%20the%20dish.%20It%20was%20readily%20accepted%20by%20the%20King%20and%20the%20people.%20After%20his%20death%2C%20when%20his%20%3Cem%3Emulazim%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(workers)%20were%20jobless%2C%20they%20went%20to%20cities%20and%20this%20biryani%20was%20spread%20in%20Kolkata%20city%20and%20became%20popular%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manzilat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCiUaf9mt1qC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCiUaf9mt1qC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCiUaf9mt1qC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Manzilat's%20(%40manzilats)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explains%20what%20sets%20the%20Awadhi%20and%20Kolkata%20biryani%20apart%20from%20the%20rest.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20nawabs%20were%20of%20%3Cem%3Enazuk%20mizaz%20%3C%2Fem%3E(delicate%20nature)%2C%20spicy%20food%20did%20not%20suit%20their%20palate.%20This%20makes%20the%20Awadhi%20food%20delicate%20and%20light%2C%20as%20well%20as%20extremely%20flavourful%20and%20aromatic%2C%20compared%20to%20Hyderabadi%2C%20Muradabadi%2C%20and%20southern%20biryanis.%20Others%20use%20a%20lot%20of%20spices%20and%20ghee.%20We%20feel%20full%20even%20after%20eating%20one%20or%20two%20%3Cem%3Elukma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mouthfuls).%20There%20is%20a%20class%20in%20Awadh%20food!%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20unique%20species%20and%20cooking%20methods%20she%20uses%20to%20cook%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261268%2Fbiryani-map-of-india-taste-the-history-find-your-favourite-among-28-versions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKolkata%20biryani%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Manzilat%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20I%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Ekorma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20I%20add%20as%20a%20layer%20in%20the%20utensil.%20After%20this%2C%20I%20add%20a%20layer%20of%20boiled%20potatoes%20savoured%20with%20ghee%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20spices.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20add%20a%20layer%20of%20boiled%20rice%20and%20add%20the%20flavouring%20of%20ghee%20and%20saffron.%20When%20you%20cook%20in%20logs%20and%20%3Cem%3Ematka%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(clay%20utensils)%2C%20it%20gives%20a%20smoky%20flavour.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cook%20biryani%20with%20regular%20spices%20like%20%3Cem%3Ekebab%20chini%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20nutmeg%2C%20%3Cem%3Eshah%20jeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20mace%2C%20cardamom%2C%20and%20clove.%20In%20some%20Awadhi%20delicacies%2C%20I%20use%20specialised%20Awadhi%20spices%20and%20herbs%20like%20%3Cem%3Epaan%20ki%20jad%2C%2