20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELearnt%20cooking%20through%20letters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzilat%20recalls%20that%20when%20she%20started%20cooking%20at%20the%20age%20of%2010%2C%20she%20was%20not%20interested%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20living%20with%20my%20father%20in%20Aligarh.%20At%20that%20time%2C%20ordering%20food%20from%20outside%20was%20not%20as%20relevant%20as%20it%20is%20today.%20So%20I%20had%20to%20cook%20along%20with%20a%20helper%20and%20would%20serve%20%3Cem%3Ekacha%20pakka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(half-cooked)%20food%20to%20my%20father.%20Sometimes%2C%20there%20would%20be%20more%20water%20in%20%3Cem%3Ekhichadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20sometimes%20rice%20would%20be%20half-cooked.%20I%20would%20fail%20to%20make%20a%20perfect%20meal%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20her%20mother%20would%20come%20to%20her%20rescue.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20used%20to%20write%20letters%20to%20us%20from%20Kolkata.%20In%20those%20letters%2C%20she%20would%20write%20a%20recipe%20and%20cooking%20method%20for%20me%20in%20Urdu.%20During%20vacations%20when%20we%20would%20be%20home%2C%20I%20used%20to%20learn%20from%20her.%20The%20first%20thing%20I%20learnt%20from%20her%20was%20%3Cem%3Eshami%20kabab%3C%2Fem%3E.%20My%20father%20relished%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20married%2C%20Manzilat%20settled%20in%20Kolkata.%20She%20loved%20to%20host%20guests%20of%20her%20husband%20and%20friends%20of%20her%20children.%20Through%20cooking%20over%20the%20years%2C%20she%20developed%20an%20immense%20interest%20in%20food.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20never%20knew%20that%20I%20would%20build%20a%20career%20in%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manzilat%20runs%20a%20home%20diner%20that%20keeps%20a%20number%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-1-1689173324-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323617%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManzilat%20runs%20a%20home%20diner%20that%20keeps%20a%20number%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20keep%20the%20legacy%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive%2C%20she%20set%20up%20Manzilat%E2%80%99s%20home%20diner%20in%20Kasba%20of%20Kolkata%20in%202018.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20nawabs%20were%20very%20fond%20of%20food%20and%20Awadhi%20cuisine%20is%20very%20popular%20but%20not%20so%20popular%20outside%20Lucknow.%20People%20even%20in%20Lucknow%20and%20Metiabruz%20do%20not%20know%20the%20history%20associated%20with%20the%20food.%20I%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20towards%20carrying%20the%20legacy%20of%20my%20family%20before%20the%20world%20forgets%20our%20lineage%20and%20the%20relevance%20of%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManzilat%20manages%20her%20home%20diner%20with%20the%20help%20of%20four%20workers%20and%20caters%20to%20foodies%20from%20across%20the%20world%2C%20including%20Japan%2C%20China%2C%20Abu%20Dhabi%2C%20Toronto%2C%20New%20Jersey%2C%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mission%20is%20not%20to%20earn%20from%20a%20commercial%20set%20up%2C%20but%20to%20spread%20awareness%20on%20the%20history%20of%20Awadh%2C%20its%20last%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah%2C%20freedom%20fighter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F156185%2Fbegum-hazrat-mahal-british-1857-mutiny%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBegum%20Hazrat%20Mahal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20our%20family%20history.%20For%20this%2C%20I%20get%20immense%20love%2C%20honour%2C%20and%20respect%2C%20which%20is%20priceless.%20That%20is%20my%20real%20earning%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689227864000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkolkata-biryani-2-1689173481.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D323582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20descendant%20of%20King%20Wajid%20Ali%20Shah%20and%20Begum%20Hazrat%20Mahal%2C%20Manzilat%20runs%20a%20home%20diner%20that%20keeps%20a%20number%20of%20royal%20delicacies%20alive%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20Kolkata%20Biryani%2C%20which%20she%20says%20has%20deep%20roots%20in%20the%20region%20of%20Lucknow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323582%2Fmanzilat-descendant-of-wajid-ali-shah-keeps-family-history-of-kolkata-biryani-alive%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20exports%20fall%20most%20in%20three%20years%20as%20global%20economy%20struggles%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689224127000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101716808%2Cimgsize-160382.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchinas-exports-fall-most-in-three-years-as-global-economy-struggles%2Farticleshow%2F101716732.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%