0our%20designs%20to%20reflect%20the%20future%2C%20and%20this%20was%20our%20guiding%20principle%20all%20the%20way.%E2%80%9D%20Mallika%20goes%20on%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20intended%20to%20create%20furniture%20of%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20waste%20gets%20a%20new%20face%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20is%20simple%20to%20understand%2C%20albeit%20tough%20to%20see%20through%20to%20the%20finish.%20But%20the%20friends%20say%20after%20the%20initial%20few%20weeks%20of%20figuring%20out%20the%20intricacies%2C%20they%20found%20a%20way%20around.%20Every%20piece%20belonging%20to%20Daera%20X%20Cancelled%20Plans%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F277009%2Fchennai-startup-how-to-make-ikea-furniture-from-cardboard-karthic-rathinam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20out%20of%20waste%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Mallika%20had%20already%20been%20doing%20this%20as%20part%20of%20her%20individual%20venture%2C%20she%20was%20familiar%20with%20the%20route%20to%20take.%20%E2%80%9CI%20develop%20different%20kinds%20of%20fabric%20from%20waste%20and%20then%20develop%20clothes%20and%20accessories%20from%20this%20fabric%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%20This%20same%20concept%20is%20used%20for%20the%20upholstery%20of%20the%20furniture%20at%20Daera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22L%20to%20R%3A%20Sharon%2C%20Mallika%20and%20Jannat%2C%20the%20trio%20behind%20the%20collaborative%20collection%20Daera%20X%20Cancelled%20Plans%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDaera-X-Cancelled-Plans-1689080816.jpg%201080