very%20minute.%20This%20practice%20contributes%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%2C%20and%20pollution%20of%20our%20oceans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20report%20stated%20that%20the%20global%20disposable%20nappy%20industry%20extracts%20over%20248%20million%20barrels%20of%20crude%20oil%20annually%2C%20and%20creates%20over%2038%20million%20tons%20of%20solid%20waste%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20about%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20disposable%20diapers%20was%20Sonika%E2%80%99s%20initiation%20into%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle%2C%20and%20there%20has%20been%20no%20going%20back.%20Today%2C%20the%20sustainability%20enthusiast%20shares%20her%20experiences%20and%20tips%20on%20zero%20waste%20practices%2C%20sustainable%20parenting%2C%20and%20leading%20an%20environmentally%20conscious%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Started%20thinking%20about%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20future%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F51NxQepHaRQ%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22How%20Sonika%20Bhasin%20started%20living%20a%20sustainable%20lifestyle%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22281%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTill%20Abir%20was%20born%2C%20our%20lifestyle%20was%20pretty%20wasteful.%20We%20realised%20that%20this%20lifestyle%20was%20not%20good%20for%20Abir%E2%80%99s%20future%20and%20decided%20to%20make%20some%20changes.%20I%20first%20started%20by%20cloth%20diapering%20Abir%20till%20he%20was%20potty%20trained.%20Why%20would%20I%20want%20to%20put%20a%20plastic%20diaper%20full%20of%20toxic%20chemicals%20on%20my%20child%3F%20I%20found%20that%20wet%20wipes%20are%20also%20made%20of%20plastic%2C%20so%20we%20di