h%20of%20authentic%20food%20made%20by%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20son%20even%20visited%20Naxalite%20villages%20to%20get%20their%20authentic%20snacks%20and%20bring%20them%20to%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20the%20tribal%20women%20in%20some%20villages%20make%20mahua%3Cem%3E%20ladoos%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20are%20made%20using%20mahua%20flower%20and%20jaggery.%20It%20is%20endemic%20to%20the%20region%20and%20is%20not%20well%20known%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAazol%20has%20been%20in%20corporation%20with%2017%20SHGs%20from%20various%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%20including%20Nandurbar%2C%20Wardha%20etc.%20Each%20of%20these%20self-help%20groups%20employs%2020%20to%20200%20women%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20acts%20as%20an%20intermediary%20between%20the%20end%20consumers%20and%20women%20in%20the%20village%20who%20make%20these%20products%20for%20them.%20Its%20wide%20range%20of%20Maharashtrian%20snacks%20includes%20various%20types%20of%20chutneys%2C%20indigenous%20rice%20like%20%3Cem%3EIndrayani%20%3C%2Fem%3Erice%2C%20spices%2C%20%3Cem%3Epapads%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Eladoos%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20products%20are%20handmade%20or%20locally%20grown%20or%20made%20using%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283463%2Fmother-daughter-natural-ghee-brand-bilona-nei-native-woman-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20recipes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20also%20fresh%20and%20preservative%20free%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Apurva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20ensure%20that%20all%20the%20women%20are%20paid%20upfront%20within%2015%20days%20of%20the%20delivery.%20We%20do%20not%20wait%20for%20the%20sale%20to%20happen%20to%20pay%20them.%20These%20women%20work%20very%20hard%2C%20and%20I%20just%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20get%20their%20fair%20share%2C%E2%80%9D%