%20immersed%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20designs%20of%20the%20classrooms%20and%20other%20rooms%20are%20made%20in%20a%20way%20that%20they%20blend%20with%20the%20nature%20outside%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saurabh%20Gupta%2C%20the%20architect%20of%20the%20building%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBringing%20nature%20to%20children%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Akanksha%20Gupta%20and%20Saurabh%20Gupta%20of%20Vijay%20Gupta%20Architects%20were%20approached%20by%20the%20school%20to%20build%20a%20school%20on%20the%2020%2C000%20square%20metre%20site%20in%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20Bannerghatta%20National%20Park%2C%20the%20duo%20knew%20that%20this%20project%20was%20going%20to%20be%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20lush%20green%20site%20with%20Bannerghatta%20Park%20close%20to%20it.%20The%20land%20had%20so%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F207906%2Fearth-heroes-environment-conservation-waste-water-wildlife-changemakers-2019-india-new-year%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emany%20trees%20and%20plantations%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20we%20did%20not%20have%20the%20heart%20to%20let%20it%20all%20be%20converted%20into%20a%20concrete%20building%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saurabh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20we%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20does%20justice%20to%20the%20land%20and%20the%20city%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20in%20the%20sense%20that%20the%20place%20has%20always%20been%20nature-loving%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20children%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20step%20out%20and%20learn%20with%20nature.%20For%20instance%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20just%20learn%20that%20rainwater%20harvesting%20exists%2C%20they%20can%20actually%20see%20it%20happening%20on%20their%20school%20campus%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-bl