hortage%20that%20you%20become%20vigilant%20about%20conserving%20it.%20I%20started%20figuring%20out%20ways%20to%20come%20up%20with%20recycling%20and%20reusing%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20corporate%20experience%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20well-paid%20job%20to%20start%20Jal%20Sevak%20Solutions%20in%202018.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20installed%20greywater%20systems%20in%2025%20places%20including%20residential%20complexes%2C%20individual%20homes%2C%20apartments%2C%20schools%2C%20hostels%2C%20office%20quarters%2C%20and%20public%20toilets%20across%2012%20cities%20including%20Kanpur%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Gorakhpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20kitchen%20sinks%20to%20toilets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijit%E2%80%99s%20low-cost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F135718%2Fgreywater-recycling-home-guide-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreywater%20recycling%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20a%20six-step%20process.%20Explaining%20how%20it%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20collect%20greywater%20from%20showers%2C%20kitchen%20sinks%2C%20washing%20machines%2C%20and%20washbasins.%20This%20greywater%20contains%20suspended%20solids%2C%20dirt%2C%20mud%2C%20nails%2C%20dissolved%20soap%2C%20and%20a%20negligible%20percentage%20of%20bacteria.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20greywater%20is%20sent%20through%20multiple%20layers%20of%20filters%20to%20remove%20all%20suspended%20solids.%20Filters%20capture%20particles%20of%20up%20to%205%20%C2%B5m%20size%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fiyuvln5Ut0E%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20filtration%2C%20Abhijit%20uses%20a%20nylon-based%20strainer%20to%20remove%20big%20particles%20like%20thread%2C%20hair%2C%20and%20paper%2C%20whereas%20another%20bucket%20filter%20comprising%20propylene%20cloth%20is%20used%20to%20clean%20the%20water%20further.%20These%20filters%2C%20which%20cost%20up%20to%20Rs%20250%2C%20require%20cleaning%20once%20a%20week%20and%20replaced%20every%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20filtered%20greywater%20is%20stored%20in%20a%20temporary%20holding%20tank%20where%20aeration%20prevents%20the%20rise%20of%20pathogens%20in%20the%20stored%20water.%20In%20step%20four%2C%20a%20pump%20carries%20water%20from%20the%20holding%20tank%20to%20a%20rooftop%20tank%2C%20and%20a%20dosing%20system%20adds%20disinfectant%20into%20the%20outlet%20manifold.%20In%20the%20fifth%20step%2C%20any%20excess%20disinfectant%20and%20residual%20solids%20in%20water%20are%20removed%20by%20passing%20the%20filtered%20and%20disinfected%20greywater%20through%20a%20final%20filtration%20stage%20of%20dechlorination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20treated%20greywater%20is%20sent%20for%20use%20in%20toilet%20flushing%2C%20floor%20cleaning%2C%20and%20gardening%20via%20dedicated%20piping.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20do%20not%20recommend%20using%20this%20water%20for%20any%20other%20activity%20as%20it%20would%20require%20other%20expensive%20multi-stage%20processes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhijit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%